(2, '中信国安国际影视特效产业基地启动仪式开幕 世界级巨匠云集', '', '6e1a00f67f62e0aa6700507dcf3fac8d.jpg', '6e1a00f67f62e0a.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">久之网讯</strong>随着数字图像技术的发展，电影特效越来越成为商业大片博取票房的重要筹码，那些全球最卖座的商业电影，基本上都是特效含量极大的电影。第五届北京国际电影节举办电影特效论坛，使得电影特效再次成为人们关注的焦点。</p><p style="margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">由中信国安影视特效产业基地承办的第五届北京国际电影节国际电影特效论坛，于2015年4月19日在位于京津冀核心区的运河第一城举行。为了实现真正的国际高端对话，中信国安特别邀请了来自好莱坞的金牌制片人汤姆•德桑托（Tom DeSanto）以及好莱坞电影特效大师杰夫•克莱泽（Jeff Kleiser）、马特•贝克 （Mat Beck）、宙奥•汉尼克 （Joel Hynek ），四位大师分别围绕“好莱坞影视特效发展与中国特效电影的国际化之路”、“电影特效工业发展与人才培养”两个论题，与来自中国的特效专家、学者进行了精彩纷呈的演讲及对话，国内来自电影界及相关院校的三百名嘉宾与会。</p><p style="margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">论坛期间，好莱坞大师们还与众多论坛嘉宾一同出席了中信国安影视特效产业基地的揭牌仪式，以及为电影大师颁发特效指导聘书在。中信国安集团总经理刘鑫同时宣布，为了打造中国电影制作的产业开放平台，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地将发起设立中国首个影视特效行业协会，并邀请上述四位好莱坞大师作为该协会的国际理事。</p><p style="margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">建设中的中信国安影视特效产业基地占地两万平方米，全部功能规划和技术标准均由好莱坞专家指导，由国内顶尖行业专家按照国际化标准亲自设计。基地配备了国际一流的全数字、网络化、集群化的影视特效制作硬件。基地除了多个国际大师级的工作室，两个1500㎡电影摄影棚，还有国际一流配置的动作捕捉棚、绿幕抠像棚、音乐录音棚、电影混录棚、电影特效制作区和实景特效教学区。同时依托功能完善的运河第一城，为客户提供影视拍摄、餐饮、住宿、娱乐、健身等五星级一体化服务。</p><p style="margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中信国安影视特效产业基地，还将与国内、外高校合作，开展学历教育、职业教育、在线教育相辅助的特效人才计划，培养国际化的影视特效人才，同时依托配套完整的产业基地，打造影视制作行业的创客基地和大学生创业基地。</p><p style="margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中信国安影视特效产业基地，位于运河第一城生态文化项目的一城文创区，地处京杭运河香河段，该项目由中信国安投资有限公司投资500亿打造，建成后，将极大改善运河沿线生态环境，完善京津冀区域生态廊道，并通过多项产业植入，实现经济的绿色、健康、可持续发展。</p><p style="margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中信国安影视特效产业基地，是代表先进电影工业的好莱坞影视特效产业力量落地中国的地方，也是中国特效精英和学子与大师零距离并肩工作的地方，这里将是好莱坞商业大片实现“中国制造”的地方，这里也将是一批真正意义的中美合拍电影诞生的地方。</p><p style="margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">借助于中信国安集团的的全方位优质资源配置，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地将成为国内最具创作优势的特效制作服务商、最具行业吸附力的影视产业基地。</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-04-19'),
(3, '国安新桥与好莱坞特效大师合作 加强国内影视特效人才培养', '', '8a08d69683a518174b9066240d94d1a9.jpg', '8a08d69683a5181.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 15px; list-style: none; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 30px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">近日，第五届北京国际电影节论坛主办方之一，国安新桥影视传媒投资有限公司邀请到美国好莱坞电影特效大师汤姆·德桑托(Tom&nbsp;DeSanto)、马特·贝克(Mat&nbsp;Beck)等几位大师共同探讨“电影工业发展”和“人才培养”的议题。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 15px; list-style: none; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 30px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在接受记者采访时，汤姆·德桑托表示，“特效不仅可以吸引观众去看一部电影，还能打破国际和文化的限制。所以我期待更多的中国的合作，因为中国的历史非常久远，可以为电影提供很多的题材。我觉得中国电影的未来非常明朗，因为中国能够很好的创作出适合观众品位的电影。这就意味说我们把很多电影背景设置在中国，然后把后期制作转到美国。我们进行这种合作，让中国的电影、中国团队能更好的走出去，和国外的团队进行合作，让他们明白国外的团队是什么样子，在不同的国家他们是如何满足不同的观众，不同观众群体的需求的。同时我们应该明白中国历史悠久尤其在制作电影方面，中国的歌剧尤其中国的京剧它博大精深，受到全世界的尊重和瞻仰，这是中国的特色。”</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 15px; list-style: none; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 30px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">马特·贝克从另一个角度说明了合作的重要性，他表示，“电影从业者不是在一个孤岛上工作，你要拍一个电影，像指挥交响乐一样，你要指挥各个部门的人员，你要有很好的眼光视觉，同时你可以通过拍照片和欣赏相关的艺术发展培养你的视觉。同时你应该有一种广阔的视野，你应该对你所从事的工作有热情，很多时候你会花大量的时候没有取得满足感。我在中国的时间比较短，在中国我看到了很多特效方面人才他们对工作所展现出来的那种热情。我希望这种热情能够保持。”</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 15px; list-style: none; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 30px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">最后，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地总经理、美国新桥传媒公司总裁屈建平补充道，“我们建立这样一个国际影视特效基地，不是简单的只想提供一个为制片服务，我们主要做的一件事就是要为中国的电影工业提供实践。作为大学教育的补充，我们愿意和电影学院、传媒大学等高等学府建立起紧密的战略合作关系。当我们有片子的时候我们能优先从大学里选拔优秀学生，在实践中培养优秀人才。我们大师不能天天待在基地，他们可以通过网络培训，也可以请一些优秀学生直接去美国到他们的工作室或者美国大学里培养，这就是我们现在人才战略计划当中的一部分。我们希望能够共同努力和中国乃至亚洲一流的院校团结起来，共同为人才培养形成一个大气侯。我们为我们的人才加油、鼓劲，想办法使中国的特效产业真正能够发展壮大，使中国电影不仅在票房上是世界第一，制作质量上也是第一。”</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 15px; list-style: none; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 30px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">据悉，中信国安影视特效基地将由中信国安投资有限公司投资500亿打造，基地除了配备国际一流的动作捕捉棚、绿幕抠像棚等硬件设施外，还会与高校合作，培养国际化的影视特效人才。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 15px; list-style: none; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 30px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这里将是好莱坞商业大片实现“中国制造”的地方，这里也将是一批真正意义的中美合拍电影诞生的地方。&nbsp;借助于中信国安集团的的全方位优质资源配置，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地将成为国内最具创作优势的特效制作服务商、最具行业吸附力的影视产业基地。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 15px; list-style: none; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 30px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-04-21'),
(4, '中信国安国际影视特效产业基地正式启动', '', 'ca1ced19327dc158ba987920e07a9032.jpg', 'ca1ced19327dc15.jpeg', '20180809', '<p class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170527/1495849001565867.jpg" title="1495849001565867.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170527093549.jpg"/></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">4月18日下午，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地在位于京津冀核心区的中信国安第一城正式启动。</span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">活动当天，众多来自好莱坞的著名电影家都参与了启动仪式，包括原迪斯尼电影公司董事长兼CEO迪克· 库克、担任过《泰坦尼克号》特效总监的特效大师马 特·贝克 （Mat Beck）、制作过《黑客帝国》、《木乃伊3》的特效大师杰奥·汉尼克 （Joel Hynek）、以及担任奥斯卡奖评委的特效大师 杰夫·克莱泽（Jeff Kleiser）、因制作《钓鱼岛真相》而闻名中国的好莱坞著名导演克里斯蒂·里比（Chris D.nebe）。启动仪式现场 还邀请了来自中国电影家协会、北京市政府、北京市教委，业界公司代表，以及中信国安集团的相关领导二十余人。</span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在启动仪式上，中信国安影视特效产业基地向到会的八位好莱坞电影专家颁发了荣誉顾问和特效指导证书，并声明在未来，这些电影大师将以中信国安影视特效基地 为平台，开展面向中国市场的国际化合作。同时中信国安影视特效产业基地还联合到会的中国特效专家、学者、影视制片人等业界人士，共同倡议成立“中国影视特 效协会”。</span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">借助于中信国安集团的的全方位优质资源配置，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地将成</span>为国内最具创作优势的特效制作服务商、最具行业吸附力的影视产业基地。</p><p class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170527/1495849011703354.jpg" title="1495849011703354.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170527093554.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-04-28'),
(10, '中信国安携好莱坞大师亮相上海电影节 中美特效合作渐入佳境', '', '3e43ba7da743ac97e049df20f4291e8a.jpg', '3e43ba7da743ac9.jpeg', '20180809', '<p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496198315614192.png" title="1496198315614192.png" alt="03745.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2015年6与15日，上海电影节期间，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地总经理、美国新桥传媒公司总裁屈建平携好莱坞特效大师杰夫·克莱泽（Jeff Kleiser）现身上海展览中心，并带来关于国安影视特效基金与好莱坞合作的最新消息。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">屈建平称，国安新桥与杰夫合作的另一部科幻大片正在筹备当中，这部电影的名字叫《Probe》,讲述了一个外星人通过植入一个地球男孩的脑中，来观察地球人的故事，而被植入的男孩也开始身负异能。据了解这部电影中会涉及到中国元素，电影完成后也会在全球市场同步发行。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/>此次国安新桥与美国特效大师之间的合作，不仅仅是单纯的项目合作，屈剑平表示，“我们建立这样一个国际影视特效基地，不是简单的只想提供一个为制片服务，我们主要做的一件事就是要为中国的电影工业提供实践。我们愿意和电影学院、传媒大学等高等学府建立起紧密的战略合作关系，在实践中培养优秀人才。我们希望能够共同努力和中国乃至亚洲一流的院校团结起来，共同为人才培养形成一个大气侯，想办法使中国的特效产业真正能够发展壮大。”</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/>杰夫也表示，此次与国安新桥合作的电影，一部分后期工作也会拿到国内来做，帮助国内的影视特效人才得到尽快成长。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/>就在4月份的北京电影节期间，中信国安影视特效产业基地的揭牌仪式在中信国安第一城举行，并为多位电影大师颁发特效指导聘书在。中信国安集团总经理刘鑫同时宣布，为了打造中国电影制作的产业开放平台，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地将发起设立中国首个影视特效行业协会，并邀请制作过《变形金刚》、《X战警》的好莱坞金牌制片人汤姆·德桑托(Tom DeSanto)、担任过《泰坦尼克号》特效总监的特效大师马特·贝克 (Mat Beck)、制作过《黑客帝国》、《木乃伊3》的特效大师杰奥·汉尼克 (Joel Hynek)、以及担任奥斯卡奖评委的特效大师杰夫·克莱泽(Jeff Kleiser)等四位好莱坞大师作为该协会的国际理事。</p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496198362161412.png" title="1496198362161412.png" alt="103904.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">据了解，建设中的中信国安影视特效产业基地占地两万平方米，全部功能规划和技术标准均由好莱坞专家指导，由国内顶尖行业专家按照国际化标准亲自设计。基地配备了国际一流的全数字、网络化、集群化的影视特效制作硬件。基地除了多个国际大师级的工作室，两个1500㎡电影摄影棚，还有国际一流配置的动作捕捉棚、绿幕抠像棚、音乐录音棚、电影混录棚、电影特效制作区和实景特效教学区。同时依托功能完善的运河第一城，为客户提供影视拍摄、餐饮、住宿、娱乐、健身等五星级一体化服务。</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/>中信国安影视特效产业基地，还将与国内、外高校合作，开展学历教育、职业教育、在线教育相辅助的特效人才计划，培养国际化的影视特效人才，同时依托配套完整的产业基地，打造影视制作行业的创客基地和大学生创业基地。</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/>中信国安影视特效产业基地，是代表先进电影工业的好莱坞影视特效产业力量落地中国的地方，也是中国特效精英和学子与大师零距离并肩工作的地方，这里将是好莱坞商业大片实现“中国制造”的地方，这里也将是一批真正意义的中美合拍电影诞生的地方。</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/>借助于中信国安集团的的全方位优质资源配置，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地将成为国内最具创作优势的特效制作服务商、最具行业吸附力的影视产业基地。（文章来源：艺恩网）</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-06-18'),
(12, '专访奥斯卡金像奖评委、好莱坞视效协会副主席杰夫·克莱泽：让特效助商业电影成功', '', '14ef83ce74472e7be92e45351c4c60b6.jpg', '14ef83ce74472e7.jpeg', '20180809', '<p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496198775211415.png" title="1496198775211415.png" alt="04512.png"/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496198783122928.png" title="1496198783122928.png" alt="541.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">南方日报上海讯 （特派记者/郑照魁）如今一提起“美国大片”，大家首先想到的就是各种大场面。“好莱坞现在很多时候，特效团队都是从编剧阶段就介入到项目当中，有时候甚至为一个好的特效场面创意，直接修改剧本，因为大家知道，很多观众进电影院就是为了视听享受。”6月15日，好莱坞视效协会副主席、奥斯卡奖评委杰夫·克莱泽接受了南方日报采访，畅谈好莱坞大制作。<br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">换思路：特效不只是技术</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">杰夫·克莱泽曾经担任过《X战警》《神奇四侠》等多部大片的特效总监。这次来到中国，是跟他的合作伙伴、中信国安影视特效产业基地的老总屈建平洽谈进一步的合作。在他看来，中国电影的确像此前一些中国导演说过的那样，在技术方面并不缺少人才，“上个月，我去了北京电影学院，发现那里培养了很多人才。我们对于中国年轻一代出现有才能的特效大师非常有信心，目前这些人只是缺乏经验。”</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在杰夫看来，除了单纯的技术层面，中国电影要想向好莱坞电影那样走向世界，必须要学会的是转变思路。“我看了一些中国电影，发现依然是导演中心制。像一些特效创意本来挺不错的，比如《唐山大地震》，但最后并没有开发好。如果按照好莱坞的做法，一开始特效团队就介入这部电影，完全可以打造出更加震撼的场景。”</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">杰夫表示，好莱坞大片目前通常的做法，都是在编剧创作阶段特效团队就已经介入，而且像声音、音乐等方面，在项目的前期就已经开始做好。而在中国，很多导演都是在电影杀青之后才开始考虑特效，单纯把特效当成技术手段。“这样就容易产生局限，很多效果必须根据演员已经完成的演出来做，但真正的大片，特效本身就是电影重要的一部分。特效的讲述方法，已经成为电影商业方面成功的灵魂元素。我所知道的，像宁浩的新片，现在就在根据特效师的建议，重新改写剧本。”</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">接地气：故事决定电影效果</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">作为好莱坞视效协会的副会长，杰夫·克莱泽并不是一个格外强调视觉效果的人。在他看来，单纯依靠视效的大片并不可取，而单纯讲故事、靠艺术性取胜的电影，同样也只能在小范围内获得认同。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">此前吴宇森从好莱坞回国，在内地拍摄了大片《赤壁》，当时他曾经表示，要把自己知道的好莱坞经验、技术带回到国内。而距离《赤壁》上映已经7年，中国的电影技术虽然有所发展，但却并没有产生质的飞越。对此，杰夫和他的合作伙伴屈建平一致认为，这并不是中国电影产业的问题，而是吴宇森带来做样本的故事题材不太合适。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">杰夫说：“我很喜欢吴宇森的《变脸》，但他的《赤壁》讲述的是一个太复杂的中国故事，世界通用的元素相对较少，所以只能在华语地区被大家接受。讲故事的方式决定了一个电影传播的效果。《赤壁》场面虽然大，但单靠特效是不可能撑起来一部电影。如果他选择的题材是一个有世界共通语言的，但又搭载了中国文化元素，应该更容易被全世界接受。”</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">以往的中国大片并没有真正“走向世界”，屈建平有很深的感慨。他表示：“当年我在美国看到《花木兰》，回国之后听到很多专家说‘那不是我们的花木兰’，其实包括《功夫熊猫》在内，但凡能在全球取得成功的电影，真的不能拘泥于单纯的中国观众思维模式。我们的导演在讲故事时，不能自说自话，要找到我们的文化和世界文化的共性所在。”</p><p></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-07-17');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(13, '高端杂志《中国城市与市长》撰文介绍中信国安国际影视特效产业基地', '', '889b5ce59b2e3c9839e923f7a510309c.jpg', '889b5ce59b2e3c9.jpeg', '20180809', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496198917544481.png" title="1496198917544481.png" alt="1104733.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">最近，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">接受了高端杂志《中国城市与市长》对我基地进行品牌推广的邀请，在</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">2015</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">年总第</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">43</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">期刊登了此次宣传的内容（图片便是刊登的宣传页面）。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">中信国安国际影视特效产业基地位于河北香河的中信国安第一城，是由中信国安投资公司与美国新桥媒体</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">(New Bridge Media USA)</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">合资创立的国际影视产业发展平台。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">在中信国安第一城，这座占地面积</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">266</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">万平方米、气势宏伟的古都风格建筑里，代表着国际化数字科技与视觉艺术完美融合的影视特效产业，拥有了中国首个产业聚集区。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">正在建设中的中信国安影视特效产业基地，占地</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">2</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">万平方米，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">旨在引入好莱坞影视特效领域的优秀人才和领先科技，打造产业形态创新、金融服务创新的影视制作业平台，服务于快速成长的中国电影工业，同时，为中国影视行业培养国际化的影视特效复合型人才。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">中信国安国际影视特效产业基地，致力于打造完善的产业基地服务配套体系，配备了国际一流的全数字、网络化、集群化的影视特效制作硬件。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">基地除了多个国际大师级的工作室，两个</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">1500</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">㎡电影摄影棚，还有国际一流配置的动作捕捉棚、绿幕抠像棚、音乐录音棚、电影混录棚、电影特效制作区和实景特效教学区。同时依托功能完善的运河第一城，为客户提供影视拍摄、餐饮、住宿、娱乐、健身等五星级一体化服务。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">中信国安影视特效产业基地，还将与国内、外高校合作，开展学历教育、职业教育、在线教育相辅助的特效人才计划，培养国际化的影视特效人才，同时依托配套完整的产业基地，打造影视制作行业的创客基地和大学生创业基地。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">中信国安影视特效产业基地，位于运河第一城生态文化项目的一城文创区，地处京杭运河香河段，该项目由中信国安投资有限公司投资</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">500</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">亿打造，建成后，将极大改善运河沿线生态环境，完善京津冀区域生态廊道，并通过多项产业植入，实现经济的绿色、健康、可持续发展。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">中信国安影视特效产业基地，是代表先进电影工业的好莱坞影视特效产业力量落地中国的地方，也是中国特效精英和学子与大师零距离并肩工作的地方，这里将是好莱坞商业大片实现“中国制造”的地方，这里也将是一批真正意义的中美合拍电影诞生的地方。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">借助于中信国安集团的的全方位优质资源配置，中信国安国际影视特效产业基地将成为国内最具创作优势的特效制作服务商、最具行业吸附力的影视产业基地。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-08-10'),
(14, '国际著名软件公司副总裁访问中信国安国际影视特效产业基地', '', '4c8984f54c00f372817a9f8ec5b6b4b1.jpg', '4c8984f54c00f37.jpeg', '20180809', '<p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496199168940459.png" title="1496199168940459.png" alt="4958.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 35px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">8</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">27</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">日上午，以影视特效制作合成软件</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">NUKE</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">闻名全球影视业的英国方准公司（</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">FOUNDRY</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">）高管访问了中信国安国际影视特效产业基地。国安新桥影视传媒投资有限公司总裁屈建平会见了该公司副总裁</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">Christopher Kenessey</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">先生和大中华区总裁俞亚敏女士。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 35px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">在会见中，双方达成了在位于第一城的影视特效基地内联合设立影视特效人才培训工作室和特效制作软件研究中心的合作意向。这将是该公司在大中华区设立的首家特效制作软件研究开发和人才培训中心。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">NUKE</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">电影特效软件是好莱坞大型特效影片制作不可或缺的利器。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">NUKE</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">曾被用在好莱坞所制作的很多电影大片中。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">NUKE<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">是由</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">The Foundry</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">公司研发的数码节点式合成软件。该软件曾获得奥斯卡奖。在数码领域，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">NUKE</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">已被用于近百部影片和数以百计的商业和音乐电视，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">NUKE</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">具有先进的将最终视觉效果与电影电视的其余部分无缝结合的能力，无论所需应用的视觉效果是什么风格或者有多复杂。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">Nuke</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">合成软件参与制作的著名影视有《泰坦尼克号》、《阿波罗</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">13</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">》、《真实的谎言》、《</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;">X</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">战警》、《变形金刚》等几乎所有著名的好莱坞特效大片。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-08-27'),
(17, '"一带一路一城国际电影展映周"即将在中信国安第一城启动', '', '40581c6b7f427936faa6ea1429f7bb7d.jpg', '40581c6b7f42793.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2013年，中国国家主席习近平提出共建“丝绸之路经济带”和“21世纪海上丝绸之路”（简称“一带一路”）的重大倡议，现已经成为中国国家战略。2014年习总书记在专题听取京津冀协同发展工作汇报时强调，要坚持优势互补、互利共赢、扎实推进，加快走出一条科学持续的协同发展路子来。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在此背景之下，由京、津、冀三地政府文化主管部门联合支持，中信国安集团发起的“一带一路一城国际文化艺术节”，将于10月1日-5日在中信国安第一城举办。</p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200236670951.png" title="1496200236670951.png" alt="1110923.png"/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">作为“一带一路一城国际文化艺术节”的系列活动，由中信国安国际影视特效产业基地联合中国电影资料馆等机构共同承办的“一带一路一城国际电影展映周”，旨在以电影为纽带，传承丝路精神，弘扬丝路文化，通过把电影艺术融入“一带一路”战略布局，推动“一带一路”共同发展。国际电影展精选了五部包括俄罗斯、哈萨克斯坦在内的沿线国家影片，以及五部票房大卖的国产影片，将在10月1日至10月5日期间系列展映。影展期间，还将搭建展线，展示丝绸之路沿途国家电影发展历程，推介丝绸之路沿途国家著名电影，将观众带进一带一路的光影之旅。</span></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200316370675.png" title="1496200316370675.png" alt="11109.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">如此精彩的“一带一路一城国际电影展”一定已经让您心动了吧！ 中信国安第一城邀你一起领略国际电影神秘又独特的魅力。艺术节正逢中秋、国庆双节，中信国安第一城还安排了更多精彩的活动，盛情招待八方来客，与大家共庆佳节。</p><p style="margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: white;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">游不尽的皇家园林，赏不完的国际电影，国安第一城邀您共度佳节！</span></strong><br/></p><p style="margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: white;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: white;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">电影展安排：</span></strong></p><p style="margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; background: white;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">时间：2015年10月1日-10月5日</span></strong></p><p style="margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; background: white;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">地点：中信国安第一城国际报告厅</span></strong></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200377700385.png" title="1496200377700385.png" alt="111216.png"/></p><p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">中信国安第一城行车路线</span></strong></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200444552958.png" title="1496200444552958.png" alt="111335.png"/></p><br/>', '0', '2015-09-19'),
(18, '中信国安国际影视特效产业基地举办一带一路一城国际电影展映周', '', 'c53b3c1a91c253a561118800bdedf18f.jpg', 'c53b3c1a91c253a.jpeg', '20180809', '<p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200581699438.png" title="1496200581699438.png" alt="11457.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">2015年9月23日，在国安宾馆举办了“一带一路一城”国际文化艺术节新闻发布会。会上由中信国安影视特效产业基地、国安新桥（北京）影视投资有限公司承办的国际电影展映周备受媒体关注。其活动承办方的负责人国安新桥影视传媒公司总经理屈建平接受了媒体采访，在采访中表示：从10月1日起，国际电影周正式启动，承办方将选取“一带一路”沿线国家的相关5部影片和中国的5部优秀影片，在中信国安第一城播放。5部“一带一路”沿线国家的影片分别来自于伊朗、土耳其、俄罗斯及阿富汗。此次选择的影片都是“一带一路”沿途国家的经典之作。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">在谈及通过电影的方式推动“一带一路”沿线国家与中国的交流时，屈建平表示，中国是第一个提出“一带一路”电影交流展映的国家，通过这次展映希望唤起中国电影界对“一带一路”沿线国家电影作品的重视。“今年是第一届，代表性和出发点是紧密配合“一带一路”的国家战略。 希望明年做成电影节，让沿线国家来推送自己的电影或纪录片”。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">据了解，本届国际文化艺术节的举办一方面是响应国家提出的“一带一路”战略，通过邀请“一带一路”沿线国家的驻华使节、文化传承人来到中国进行交流访问，加强彼此之间的了解。另一方面，本届国际文化艺术节也是响应京津冀协同发展的号召，特别突出“一城”的概念，力图把中信国安第一城以及其所在地河北香河打造成为京津冀三地资源共享、优势互补的典型案例，进而发展成为京津冀与“一带一路”沿线国家交流沟通的文化纽带。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">彰显责任感 企业用行动实践国家战略</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">“一带一路一城”国际文化艺术节的举办，也展示中信国安集团作为国有大型企业对国家战略发展的关注和支持，并积极响应国家的战略的发展方向，为“一带一路”发展战略贡献力量。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">中信国安集团相关负责人表示，“国有文化企业要有责任、有担当，国家战略最终依然是要靠企业的力量去推广和实现，尤其是在“一带一路”大战略下，通过企业市场化的运作，能够形成“一带一路”沿线国家相关企业的紧密联盟，形成一个稳固的经济共同体，进而才能够让文化的交流更加通畅，更加便利。”</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">该负责人同时表示，中信国安第一城落户河北香河，本身也是企业贯彻京津冀协同发展战略的一个案例，通过实践证明，紧跟国家大战略走，企业才能获得发展先机，国有企业才能够将自己的利益与国家的利益始终保持一致，让企业健康发展的同时，让国家战略顺利实施。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">同时，中信国安第一城作为“一带一路一城”国际文化艺术节的举办地，致力于以文化艺术为核心，推动“一带一路”经济带国家的交融与发展，并通过此次系列主题活动的举办，为未来“一带一路”沿线国家开展文化、贸易活动奠定基础，不仅要在中信国安第一城举办此类主题活动，还要到“一带一路”沿线国家的重点城市举办一系列的文化活动，使文化成为交融的纽带，实现共建共享共赢，推动“一带一路”沿线国家相关产业的发展。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-09-24'),
(19, '中信国安投资有限公司携手北京电影学院打造国际化影视产业共同体', '', '836cacd9a54be177c049cdb24def9218.jpg', '836cacd9a54be17.jpeg', '20180809', '<p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中信国安投资有限公司（以下简称“国安投资”）与北京电影学院（以下简称“北电”）日前就共同促进影视多元化合作和产业落地达成友好共识，并将携手共建影视产业基金、影视新媒体学院、影视制作中心等影视战略规划，不久就将以此为契机开展一系列的产业合作。通过产业合作，“国安投资“和“北电“都将整合各方资源，发挥各自资源优势，开展线上线下的影视项目全方位合作。</span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200676120265.png" title="1496200676120265.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200689992312.png" title="1496200689992312.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">通过此次合作，“国安投资”与“北电”将共同发起组建影视产业基金。该基金通过整合电影产业相关资源，主要用于扶持青年电影人才创业及中信国安第一城的影视创客空间，培养优秀青年导演、演员、编剧以及开展国际化合作。</span></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200713136944.png" title="1496200713136944.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200726565179.png" title="1496200726565179.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">与此同时，在中信国安第一城还将共建“北京电影学院青年电影人才培训基地”和“北京电影学院产学研创作实践基地”，基地还将组建影视新媒体学院，就人才培训和教学实践展开多方合作。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200749148545.png" title="1496200749148545.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200764598744.png" title="1496200764598744.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">此外，“国安投资”和“北电”还将共建“影视制作中心”，建成后的影视制作中心还将把“北电“强大的师资、团体等内部资源发挥到极致，在企业影视项目的拍摄、影视特效和后期制作等方面开展全方位的合作。</p><p><br/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200787595559.png" title="1496200787595559.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">北京电影学院是中国唯一、亚洲最大、世界知名的电影专业高等院校，是北京市主管、国家新闻出版广电总局和教育部重点支持建设的艺术院校。</span><br/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496200811103715.png" title="1496200811103715.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">中信国安投资有限公司将依托京津冀核心区打造影视文化园，开展影视教育、影视制作、影视文化园区建设等经营事项。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2015-10-26');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(22, '英国FOUNDRY公司总裁访问中信国安国际影视特效产业基地', '', 'ae321e9149b13162aec2b6cb16706fd3.jpg', 'ae321e9149b1316.jpeg', '20180809', '<p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170531/1496201280856633.png" title="1496201280856633.png" alt="2637.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal;">月24日下午，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">全球著名的影视</span>特效制作软件公司——英国FOUNDRY公司总裁专程访问了<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">国安新桥（北京）影视传媒投资有限公司。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">FOUNDRY公司的总裁Bill Collis先生</span>与新桥影视公司的总裁屈建平(John Qu)先生就共同开展影视特效人才的培训等合作项目进行了友好会谈。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; 在会谈中，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal;">双方就在中国影视特效制作人才的高端定制化培训方面明确了合作方向。</span></strong></span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal;">屈总还向<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">Bill</span>总裁介绍了在<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">位于中信国安第一城即将落成的中信国安国际影视特效产业基地的基本情况。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: normal;">屈总</span></strong></span></strong>告诉<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">Bill</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">总裁，</span>该基地是集合了国际一流的全数字、网络化、集群化的全球影视特效制作中心。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">Bill</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">总裁表示十分期待下次来华时能到国安第一城的影视特效产业基地参观访问。</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px