(79, '国安新桥影视特效培训学院', '', '73f0628995e4eb6fcf563d9e0715bbbc.jpg', '73f0628995e4eb6.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑">&nbsp;&nbsp; 国安新桥影视特效培训学院是中信国安集团旗下电影特效相关职业教育的高端品牌，依托产业基地，由中信国安集团倾力打造的国内电影特效大师孵化器！我们以中国电影工业的崛起为己任，伴着一颗“匠”心来培养中国高级影视特效人才。校址位于京津冀核心区的国家</span><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: black">4A</span><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑">级景区中信国安第一城。</span></span></p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170602/1496347520863599.png" title="1496347520863599.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br/></p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: black;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px">“学院”着眼于国内外影视市场的动态分析，致力于复合型影视制作人才的发掘培养。将国内外影视特效、角色动画、后期合成、视效制片等专业课程作为重点内容，采用理论与实践相结合的教学方式，建立起科学、实效、完备的课程体系。</span></p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, san