rd !important;letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 18px"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 16px;line-height: 26px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;text-indent: 28px;letter-spacing: normal;word-spacing: 0px;widows: 1;font-stretch: normal;float: none;display: inline !important;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">坛</span></span><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 16px;line-height: 26px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;text-indent: 28px;letter-spacing: normal;word-spacing: 0px;widows: 1;font-stretch: normal;float: none;display: inline !important;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">结束后，中外合拍中国文化IP电影签约仪式的在活动现场举办。好莱坞著名制片人汤姆德桑托与中信国安集团有限公司副总经理、中信国安文化传媒有限公司董事长崔明宏，在中信国安集团有限公司董事长李士林，中信国安集团有限公司党委书记夏桂兰，中信国安集团有限公司总经理刘鑫等见证下进行了签约。<span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 16px;line-height: 26px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 28px;letter-spacing: normal;word-spacing: 0px;widows: 1;font-stretch: normal;float: none;display: inline !important;background-color: rgb(255, 218, 81)">中信国安拟出资1.2亿美元投资中美合拍IP影视项目</span>。</span></span></p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant