/20170602/1496347304357320.png" title="1496347304357320.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170602/1496347287280587.png" title="1496347287280587.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170602/1496347273273120.png" title="1496347273273120.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170602/1496347257471234.png" title="1496347257471234.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br/></p><hr/><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><br/></p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">那么，说了这么多，我们究竟想干嘛？？？</p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">第一、中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地制作部急着要用人。</p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">第二、“基地”为目前的电影项目及将来与Tom Desanto合拍中国IP电影项目储备人才。</p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">总之，我们只要两种人：</p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">一、能干！</p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">二、我们培养你一阵子，你变得能干！</p><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 25.6000003814697px;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">我们的课程大纲在上面已经呈上，如果你感兴趣，就来。我们的招生对象要求没那么复杂，<span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;wor