: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; line-height: 11.5200004577637px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 熟练运用 Nuke 等后期合成软件，能够匹配 CG 与实拍素材的光影，制作写实级别的镜头；精通三维分层合成，熟悉立体合成，三维合成等技术；能承受较大的工作压力；了解相关三维软件优先；有相关工作经验优先。 &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px;">&nbsp;</span></p></td></tr><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 97px;"><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 7px; word-wrap: break-word !important; word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) windowtext windowtext; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;" width="101"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">视效制片师</span></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 7px; word-wrap: break-word !important; word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) windowtext windowtext rgb(221, 221, 221); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;" width="457" valign="top"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; line-height: 12.4799995422363px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; line-height: 11.5200004577637px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp;有一定的视效制作相关工作经验，了解制作各个环节相关技术指标；具有相关视效制片工作经验；有清晰的项目管理和时间管理概念；极强的沟通能力，善于情绪管理；能承受较大工作压力，能接受加班。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">表1</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; line-height: 34.5999984741211px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">1.人才储备进入流程</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">A<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">面向社会招聘，聘用具有多年行业制作经验的业内精英。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">B<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">面向校园招聘，聘用对影视特效行业感兴趣且具有发展潜力的学生。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 28px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;注释：</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;如果应聘者不具备储备条件，但对影视特效制作行业感兴趣者，可经过 20-36 周不等 的储备训练，经考试合格后，同样可以进入基地人才储备库！&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170602/1496346903996743.png" title="1496346903996743.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 31.1399993896484px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 34.5999984741211px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">&nbsp;2.人才出口</span></span></h3><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">（1）基地储备的合格技术人才，可在基地任职相关工作，并有机会参与到中美合拍项目的制作当中去。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px