ackground-color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">三、“学费无忧计划”介绍</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 由学院合作金融机构为有志于从事影视特效行业的优质学员提供“学费无忧”无抵押贷款服务，还款期限1年（自贷款发放后的第4个月开始还款，学院为学员提供商业实训补贴辅助学员还款），该贷款仅用于缴付学费。由学员提供个人资料，经金融机构征信审核合格后实时放贷。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-decoration: none; background-color: rgb(165, 200, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="background-color: rgb(165, 200, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: 宋体;">贷款申请资料：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">　1、年满十八周岁，具有完全民事行为能力；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">　2、居民身份证原件及复印件（有效期必须大于6个月）；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">&nbsp;&nbsp; 3、学历证书原件及复印件，在校学生需提供学生证（国家承认、学信网可查）；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">　4、相关银行的有效银行卡；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">　5、与学院签署的相关培训协议。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">四、就业无忧</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 学员毕业考核合格后，入职基地分公司就业。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">五、薪资待遇</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 20.8px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 20.8px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 新入职员工按照实际岗位、考核成绩和工作能力进行薪资定级，享有与分公司同级员工同等的福利待遇。同时为入职学员提供同等的晋升通道，依照分公司的晋升机制，经相应考核合格后即可逐级晋升。</span></p>', '1', '2017-05-18');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(83, '王晶导演考察中信国安新桥影视基地  计划在一城打造电影巨制', '王晶导演考察中信国安新桥影视基地  面对影视基地先进的电影全流程制作硬件和中外艺术家组成的电影特效制作团队，王导表示出极大的合作意愿。', '7eee172c980c4c111d6bdceefb297e52.jpg', '7eee172c980c4c1.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170609/1496951467599497.jpg" title="1496951467599497.jpg" alt="1.jpg"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 40px;line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">6</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">月7日,香港著名导演王晶专程莅临中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地考察，面对影视基地先进的电影全流程制作硬件和中外艺术家组成的电影特效制作团队，王导表示出极大的合作意愿。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170609/1496951479164140.jpg" title="1496951479164140.jpg" alt="1496951479164140.jpg" width="800" height="484"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 40px;line-height: 200%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">在与中信国安集团总经理刘鑫的工作会谈中，王晶导演明确表示，愿意在中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地和中信国安第一城拍摄两部大片，并就共同开发新一代电影互动体验项目进行了深度沟通。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170609/1496951490401923.jpg" title="1496951490401923.jpg" alt="1496951490401923.jpg" width="800" height="534"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">在影视制作基地，中信国安一城控股有限公司董事长姜玉明、中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总裁屈建平陪同王晶导演参观了新近落成的大型摄影棚和动作捕捉棚。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170609/1496951596630205.jpg" title="1496951596630205.jpg" alt="1496951596630205.jpg" width="800" height="542"/></p><p style="line-height: 200%">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">在参观多功能摄影棚时，影视基地总裁屈建平向王导介绍，这些摄影棚设计建造规格很高，棚内全面满足同期录音的需求，配备了空调静音系统，由于影棚温度可控，具备反季节拍摄的相关条件。王导对大型摄影棚具备的多用途特效拍摄及雨淋系统表示了浓厚的兴趣，对基地将进入的现场拍摄、演员表演与特效场景的实时合成表示期待。</span><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170609/1496951654106264.jpg" title="1496951654106264.jpg" alt="1496951654106264.jpg" width="800" height="464"/></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">王导还与影视基地的艺术家们讨论了有关特效拍摄、动作捕捉及运动摄影控制数据存储等问题。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170609/1496951682489316.jpg" title="1496951682489316.jpg" alt="1496951682489316.jpg" width="800" height="430"/></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">*</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">王晶导演简介：王晶，香港影视导演、编剧、制作人，毕业于香港中文大学中文系。1977年，编写了第一部电影剧本《鬼马狂潮》。1978年到1986年期间，编过40多部电影剧本。1981年首次执导电影《千王斗千霸》。1997年联同文隽等成立最佳拍档电影公司。从影以来，出自他手中的电影作品多达近200部。电影代表作有：《赌神系列》、《赌侠》、《九品芝麻官》、《天下第一》、《大上海》、《澳门风云》等。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170609/1496951710145955.jpg" title="1496951710145955.jpg" alt="7.jpg"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p style="line-height: 150%"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 150%"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">特别鸣谢：</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">照片摄影：中信国安第一城-张新广；</span></p><p style="line-height: 150%"><strong><span style="line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">注：</span></strong><span style="line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">照片摄影：中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地-Chris Wen</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 28px;">&nbsp; 撰稿编辑：中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地-Lexy Xie。</span></p><p style="line-height: 150%"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 150%"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 150%"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">来源:</span></strong><span style="line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">中信国安国际影视特效产业基地</span></p><p style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体">国安新桥(北京)影视传媒投资有限公司</span></p>', '0', '2017-06-08'),
(84, '银川互联网电影节将与中信国安影视特效产业基地合作', '首届银川互联网电影节将于10月15日在银川开幕。电影节将与中信国安影视特效产业基地合作，为互联网影视作品的制作保驾护航。', '301a57c03c1674fca76423d54beb58a0.jpg', '301a57c03c1674f.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;首届银川互联网电影节将于10月15日在银川开幕。电影节以“智慧银川、影视中国、互联发展”为主题，以“搭建互联网电影交流展示发展平台，推进互联网电影的发展”为宗旨，鼓励和扶持互联网电影、互联网影视剧、导演新人，奖励优秀创作团队。导演张纪中将担任电影节“金杞奖”评委会主席。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; line-height: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 此次电影节，包括精选互联网电影放映、网络视听产业论坛、影视特效与技术论坛、成立中国影视知识管理联盟专业委员会、互联网影视金融与模式探索高峰论坛、“金杞奖”评选等十余项主体活动。值得一提的是，电影节将成立的中国影视知识联盟委员会，建立行业标准，推动中国互联网影视产业进一步高速发展。此外，电影节将与中信国安影视特效产业基地合作，为互联网影视作品的制作保驾护航。</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2017-06-13'),
(85, '国安新桥影视特效产业基地出席上海国际电影节', '中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总裁屈建平先生，副总经理黄鹤先生等一行拜访上海国际电影节恒信文化产业集团电影市场展台。', 'f6677396a04e95422104ba7115677664.jpg', 'f6677396a04e954.jpeg', '20180809', '<p><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">6月17日，第二十届上海国际电影节正式拉开帷幕。除了最耀眼的金爵奖评选以及国际影展之外，对于不少电影人来说，产业板块无疑是上海国际电影节最吸引人的部分。恒信文化产业集团首次携强势IP亮相上海国际电影节·电影市场板块，重点展示包括年代黑帮电影《江湖影帝》、好莱坞动画史诗电影《THE ARK &amp; THE AARDVARK》（《诺亚方舟》暂译）在内的12个主控项目。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">电影市场板块刚开展，位于上海展览馆东一馆二层的恒信文化产业集团独立展厅就备受关注， 宸铭传媒董事长兼CEO董宸辰先生，宸铭传媒董事兼副总裁陈爽先生，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总裁屈建平先生，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地副总经理黄鹤先生，中国电影基金会吴天明青年电影专项基金总监吴妍妍女士，中国电影基金会吴天明青年电影专项基金运营总监吴珂女士，北京高空秋千影视文化传播有限公司创始人、著名制片人曹欣先生、电影《我是马布里》制片人韩肯女士、导演杨子先生、美国制片人Jeff Sharp&nbsp;先生等众多业内著名电影人前来观展，并与恒信文化总裁石峰先生、副总裁杨宇农女士就项目合作、资源打通及战略捆绑等方面进行深入交流。</span><br/></span><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170622/1498083921296719.jpg" title="1498083921296719.jpg" alt="1498083921296719.jpg" width="1039" height="688"/></span><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(126, 126, 126); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> <br/></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(126, 126, 126); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(126, 126, 126); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总裁屈建平先生一行人前来观展】</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(126, 126, 126); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></span></p><p style="margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(0, 209, 0);">内容为王 整合全球影视资源</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 29px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">在内容为王的时代，恒信文化作为恒信进军娱乐产业的重要板块，在开发优质IP版权的同时联手业内外优势资源，以国际化视角打造全产业链深度合作。</span></p><p style="margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">在不久前刚刚结束的戛纳电影节上，恒信文化携好莱坞史诗动画《诺亚方舟》高调亮相。作为《诺亚方舟》的主要投资公司，恒信文化力求在保证影片品质的同时，最大限度的提升故事的可看性。而《诺亚方舟》作为好莱坞有史以来第一部由中国主投资的史诗动画巨作，彰显了恒信文化整合全球影视文化产业资源的卓著努力和决心。</span></p><p style="margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">除此之外，本次上海电影节，恒信文化还推出了超现实动作喜剧电影《返祖之通天大圣》、玄幻类网游同名电视剧《仙侠世界》、魔幻古装动画电影《龙族之龙之说》、古装玄幻电影《神笔之笔下乾坤》、奇幻探案电影《九州之黑暗之子》、警匪动作电影《玩命救赎》、年代黑帮电影《江湖影帝》、现代爱情电影《十一天零一夜》、刑侦科幻都市喜剧《复古神探》、玄幻古装动作电影《绝天》和爱情网络剧《良辰多喜欢》等多个优质项目，题材囊括了动作、冒险、科幻、爱情等多维度元素。</span></p><p style="margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 209, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(0, 209, 0);">深耕电影领域 积极开拓新格局</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">恒信文化是恒信投资的一家独立运营的文化集团，由恒信影业、恒信动漫、恒信传播、恒信国际四大分公司构成。2016年，恒信文化开始与灯塔影业、索尼影业、漫威、福克斯、派拉蒙等美国顶级精品电影公司展开深度战略合作，并以影视研发、制作、投资为业务核心，在采购、开发优质IP版权的同时，投资、制作优质文化产业项目，全面覆盖影视、动漫、网生、游戏、经纪等资源。</span></p><pre style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">恒信文化集团总裁石峰在上海电影节期间接受上海交通广播电台专访时表示，恒信天然的品牌优势，让恒信文化从起步阶段就具有充分的市场接纳能力。创始人团队都是影视文化行业内资深的电影人，深耕影视文娱行业十余载，积累了广泛、优质的行业资源和人脉。在符合市场原则的大前提之下，借助恒信钻石的资本助力，使得恒信文化在初创阶段一路加速奔驰。</pre><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; font-stretch: normal; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">纵览当下的文化产业市场，唯有真正打通全产业链业务模式，才能先人一步抢占先机。恒信文化作为恒信集团进军文化产业的重要板块，以前瞻性视野开启全新的产业版块整合与产业生态链延伸，凭借强大的泛娱乐战略布局，势要开拓文化产业发展新格局。</span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; font-stretch: normal; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; font-stretch: normal; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">来源:网易</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2017-06-17'),
(86, '中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地助力上海国际电影节峰会', '2017年6月19日，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总经理屈建平先生作为主讲嘉宾受邀参加上海国际电影节“量子云影视云计算峰会”。', '2748803985d992cee81bb28debd05e17.jpg', '2748803985d992c.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 16px;">2017<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">年</span>6<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">月</span>19日<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">，由上海国际电影节和量子云未来信息科技有限公司共同主办的</span>“<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">量子云影视云计算峰会</span>”在<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">上海展览中心隆重召开。中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总经理屈建平先生作为主讲嘉宾受邀参加，宁夏石嘴山市大武口区人民政府区长苏焕喜、宁波影视文化产业区（象山影视城）管委会主任陈建瑜、无锡国家数字电影产业园总经理施娟、青岛万达东方影都技术部总经理郑碎尧、微影资本合伙人徐东升、华夏幸福基业影视文化产业负责人李颖、量子云</span>COO汪洋泽等影视行业公司高管及政府领导<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">也参加了了此次峰会论坛。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170622/1498084971307013.png" title="1498084971307013.png" alt="1498084971307013.png" width="1039" height="580"/></p><p style="margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-weight: bold;">中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总经理：屈建平（左三）</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">“量子云影视云计算峰会”围绕影视文化技术升级共设四大板块：媒体分发网络：“重塑边缘上的媒体云”、“影视云如何助力影视小镇3.0”、“画面之外 艺术之上”以及“量子云的内容之路”。随着影视产业的不断发展与升级，影视小镇随之“风生水起”，必然带来机遇与挑战。在影视热点的带动下，影视小镇打破了起初的影视基地高耗资建造实景的发展模式，融合了影视拍摄及后期制作，并且以影视产业为纽带的生产链将得到充分发展。此次“量子云圆桌对话：影视云如何助力影视小镇”邀请到了国内顶级影视园区的实践者，主讲嘉宾各抒己见，分享了各自在打造影视产业园区过程中的成功经验。</p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170622/1498084434636180.png" title="1498084434636180.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总经理屈建平先生作为与会的重要嘉宾，也就中国电影工业化和人才培养发表了看法。中信国安自2014年以来，着力开始布局国际化影视业。作为中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地的投资运营主体，基地自</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">2014</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">年建立以来一直致力于打造国际化的电影特效及影视后期制作产业核心力量。基地以</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;">“</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">用世界的语言</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">讲中国的故事</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">”</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">为使命，整合国际先进影视资源，打造中国文化</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">IP</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">电影。力争把</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;">“</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">中国文化</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">IP</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">电影</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">”</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">推向世界市场，增强中华文化在世界的感召力和影响力为己任。</span></span><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170622/1498084481658099.png" title="1498084481658099.png" alt="图片.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-weight: bold;">中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总经理：屈建平（左三）</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">屈总还指出，“量子云未来科技与中信国安的未来合作，将为具备了功能性，艺术性及技术性三位一体化的中国影视特效产业基地树立标杆，为推动中国影视产业工业化进程保驾护航！”让我们共同期待着中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地的全面启航，在“一带一路”的大背景下与众多企业一道协同发展，助力影视行业高速发展，让更多的高质量中国影视作品迈向国际舞台，进一步增进中国文化与世界的交流，真正成为中国电影的“梦工厂”！</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2017-06-19'),
(87, '中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地再次亮相上海国际电影节', '中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地再次亮相中国唯一的国际A类电影节，第二十届上海国际电影节市场展，与同行互动热络，收获颇丰。', '1c8473497d884e2bc9dc9cb6eb50f022.jpg', '1c8473497d884e2.jpeg', '20180809', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;作为中国唯一的国际A类电影节，第二十届上海国际电影节受到全球瞩目，电影市场展更是国内外厂商云集，新秀辈出。中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地再次亮相电影市场展，与同行互动热络，收获颇丰。电影节期间，特效基地领导与英国松林集团董事长会晤达成深度合作意向、与战略合作伙伴“恒信文化产业集团”就具体项目合作进行磋商、与上海湛旺影业有限公司建立战略合作。</p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500028490386.jpg" title="1498500028490386.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095243.jpg"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地亮相上影节市场。</p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500057731675.jpg" title="1498500057731675.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095252.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地参展团队，与到访的海内外嘉宾热忱交流、洽商合作</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500195172541.jpg" title="1498500195172541.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095257.jpg"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;电影节期间，英国松林集团董事长Paul Golding一行专程到访，与特效基地领导就此前双方团队对接中的影视制作、影视金融等合作意向进一步磋商。会谈中，松林集团董事长表示期待在近期访问位于中信国安第一城的影视特效产业基地。中信国安文化传媒有限公司副总经理高传华先生、中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总经理屈建平先生表示十分期待与松林集团进行的全面合作，并欢迎Paul董事长在近期访问基地。</p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500233503030.jpg" title="1498500233503030.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095301.jpg"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 松林集团，成立于1936年，是英国最大的电影制作基地和世界先进的电影制作中心。该集团拥有至少40多间各类摄影棚和10多间数码电视摄制室，室外提供多种多样的外景地。现有300多家电影制作公司落户于此，一年产值为70多亿美元。在加拿大、多米尼加、印度尼西亚等国设有分公司。该集团制作的电影已超过1500部。其中，制作的知名电影“007系列”既是松林集团的辉煌，也是英国电影史上的标志性产品。</p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500568981795.jpg" title="1498500568981795.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095306.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>基地一行与战略合作伙伴恒信文化产业集团就具体项目合作进行会晤</strong></span></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500627808952.jpg" title="1498500627808952.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095310.jpg"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;今年3月份，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地与恒信文化产业集团结成了战略合作伙伴关系。为落实合作协议，上海电影节期间，国安新桥影视基地总经理屈建平与恒信文化产业集团联合创始人兼总裁石峰先生一行就下一步在影视项目合作、资源互换及战略规划等方面进行了深入交流。双方表示将积极推进，落实下一步深度合作，部分具体合作项目也将陆续展开。</p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500640499762.jpg" title="1498500640499762.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095313.jpg"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;恒信文化是恒信投资的一家独立运营的文化集团，由恒信影业、恒信动漫、恒信传播、恒信国际四大分公司构成。2016年，恒信文化开始与灯塔影业、索尼影业、漫威、福克斯、派拉蒙等美国顶级精品电影公司展开深度战略合作，并以影视研发、制作、投资为业务核心，在采购、开发优质IP版权的同时，投资、制作优质文化产业项目，全面覆盖影视、动漫、网生、游戏、经纪等资源。</p><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="text-decoration-line: underline;"><strong>基地一行访问上海湛旺影业有限公司展位 双方建立战略合作</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500667505884.jpg" title="1498500667505884.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095318.jpg"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在湛旺影业的展位，上海湛旺影业有限公司董事长裘立新与基地一行进行了深入交流。裘董事长表示，目前公司多个电影项目已陆续启动。希望能够更好地运用好莱坞技术创造出具有东方神韵的“新神话”。在会谈中，双方就影视拍摄、影视后期制作等方向达成了合作意向并准备于近期落实战略合作。<img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170627/1498500752364716.jpg" title="1498500752364716.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170627095321.jpg"/></p>', '0', '2017-06-21');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(88, '恒信文化产业集团到访中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地', '7月12日，恒信文化产业集团的领导一行，莅临中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地考察，双方就影视基金和制作项目落地展开了全面深入的会谈。', '6a884cbc88aae65046ce5290bf5dcd8a.jpg', '6a884cbc88aae65.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">7</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">月12日，恒信文化产业集团联合创始人、总裁石峰先生，恒信文化产业集团联合创始人、常务副总裁杨宇农女士，以及香港著名导演范秀明先生等一行，莅临中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地考察，双方就影视基金和制作项目落地展开了全面深入的会谈。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504568796809023.jpg" title="1504568796809023.jpg" alt="1.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">恒信文化产业集团代表团与</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">中信国安新桥影视基地领导合影</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总裁屈建平陪同恒信影业一行领导及艺术家首先参观了新近落成的大型摄影棚，动作捕捉棚，杜比录音剧院和调音调色棚，面对影视基地先进的电影全流程制作硬件和中外艺术家组成的专业电影特效制作团队，恒信文化产业集团领导表示出极大的合作意愿。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504568810427237.jpg" title="1504568810427237.jpg" alt="2.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">中信国安新桥影视基地总裁屈建平先生（右一）、副总经理黄鹤先生（右二）向恒信文化产业集团总裁石峰先生（左二）、</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">范秀明导演（左一）介绍基地摄影棚</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在参观大型多功能摄影棚时，影视基地总裁屈建平向来访人员介绍到，这些摄影棚设计由美国华纳兄弟影业的影棚设计师指导，国内一流设计团队操刀设计，棚内全面满足现场搭景拍摄，同期录音等各类影视拍摄需求。石总，范导对大型摄影棚具备的多用途特效拍摄及雨淋系统赞赏有加，并对基地即将引入的现场拍摄与特效场景的实时渲染合成表示期待。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170714/1499982231268693.png" title="1499982231268693.png" alt="image.png" width="644" height="500"/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">中信国安新桥影视基地常务副总经理杨晓彬先生（右二），基地运营部总监贾宗达先生（右一）向恒信文化产业集团常务副总裁</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">杨宇农女士（左一）、恒信影业副总经理刘海燕女士（左二）介绍基地摄影棚</span></strong><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">在与中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地总裁屈建平先生的工作会谈中，石峰总表示，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地是恒信文化集团的战略伙伴，基地配备的国际一流的全数字、网络化、集群化的电影特效制作硬件以及影视后期音视频制作系统将是恒信电影项目制作的有力保障，双方的合作是相辅相成互惠互利的，期待共同成立影视基金打造影视项目。屈总也同时指出，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地和恒信文化产业集团的全面战略合作是“1+1+世界”，可以采取多种灵活的合作方式，与全球影视大咖共同打造中国影视行业的旗舰。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">*恒信文化产业集团联合创始人、总裁石峰简介：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170714/1499982501182905.jpg" title="1499982501182905.jpg" alt="石峰.jpg"/><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">毕业于中国传媒大学，硕士学历。是业内知名制片人，拥有十余年制片人经验，曾操盘多个影视项目，包括《诺亚方舟》、《摆渡人》、《欧洲攻略》、《绝世高手》、《南极绝恋》、《牧人》、《莽荒记》等优秀作品。其担当制片的华语电影《不怕贼惦记》(2011年)入选第24届东京电影节“亚洲之风”单元。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !impor