word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">来源</span>:<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地</span></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">国安新桥</span>(北京)影视传媒投资有限公司</span></span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2017-07-13');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(89, '廊坊市文化产业发展现场交流会在中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地召开', '8月23日,廊坊市文化产业发展现场交流会、全市宣传部长会议在香河县召开,河北省廊坊市委宣传部长王曦等相关负责同志一行专程来到中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地视察工作。', 'effdd61ccf695077133617be3924ee68.jpg', 'effdd61ccf69507.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504568290228126.jpg" title="1504568290228126.jpg" alt="1.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为早日实现由文化资源大省向文化强省的跨越，河北省廊坊市坚持扶持重点项目、培育新兴业态、聚集园区经济，全力促进文化与科技的深度融合，大力发展文化创意产业。8月23日,廊坊市文化产业发展现场交流会、全市宣传部长会议在香河县召开,河北省廊坊市委常委、宣传部长、统战部长王曦，河北省香河县委书记李桂强，以及市直和各县（市、区）等相关负责同志一行专程来到中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地视察工作。作为香河县文化产业发展的核心项目，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地的建设与发展一直以来都离不开各级领导和行业同仁的关心支持。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">王曦部长、李桂强书记及市直和各县（市、区）等相关负责同志在中信国安第一城投资控股有限公司董事长姜玉明先生、中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地运营部总监贾宗达先生及相关人员的陪同下视察了基地。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504568341523913.jpg" title="1504568341523913.jpg" alt="2.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在参观基地的影棚时，基地运营部的贾总介绍说：“作为中信国安拓展影视文化产业的重点投资项目，基地的一期、二期工程已全部落成并已陆续承接了多部影视制作项目。截止到目前，基地参与特效制作的影视项目包括：院线电影《二代妖精》、《时间牢笼》、《大闹东海》等；电视剧《凤凰无双》、《武动乾坤》等”。王曦部长对基地达到国际化标准的摄影棚赞叹不已，他说道：“这应该是目前环北京技术规格最高的摄影棚了！”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“在这样一个优秀项目稀缺的时代，能拍出好电影的项目并不多，有好的IP能把它影视化，尤其是电影化，没有专业化的硬件、软件及团队是根本做不到的！“贾总进一步介绍说，“一部《战狼2》目前能够收获50多亿的票房，也是邀请到了专业的国际化后期团队来参与把控影片的制作水准！我们中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地全部功能布局和技术标准均由好莱坞专家指导、国内顶尖行业专家参与设计。基地致力于打造全流程的影视制作服务体系，配备了国际一流的全数字、网络化、集群化的电影特效制作硬件以及影视后期音视频制作系统。涵盖包括大型数字电影摄影棚、动作捕捉棚、虚拟绿幕棚、杜比Atmos全景声电影混录棚、DI调色棚、大型交响乐录音棚、动效棚、音视频剪辑工作站、特效后期制作区、影视特效教学区和特效集群渲染区等。依托功能完善的中信国安第一城，特效基地同时还能为剧组提供影视拍摄、制作、餐饮、住宿等一体化服务“。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504568512903361.jpg" title="1504568512903361.jpg" alt="3.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">此外，王曦部长、李桂强书记一行还深入考察了基地的数字特效制作区，了解目前基地制作的基本概况和数字资产等情况。看到基地的艺术家们正在制作的工作场景时，王曦部长不禁感叹：“要大力发展廊坊文化产业，要做就做中国最好的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">重工业</span>电影！”当李桂强书记了解到随着优秀项目的层出不穷，现在的影视特效技术发展也会不断推陈出新时感慨地说：“通过不断承接的制作业务，期待着你们基地能够更好地运用好莱坞式的技术标准进行流程化管理，为提升中国电影制作工业化水平做出自己应有的贡献！”</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504568524143189.jpg" title="1504568524143189.jpg" alt="4.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">文化创意行业的发展，离不开创新和科技的进步，同时必须放眼世界，积极开拓国际文化市场，与国际接轨，提高文化创意产业的竞争力、影响力和吸引力。中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地作为国际化的影视工业制作中心，正日益彰显出它的产业实力与文化魅力，成为一道亮眼的城市名片。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504568583187951.jpg" title="1504568583187951.jpg" alt="5.jpg"/></p>', '0', '2017-08-24'),
(90, '第十三届“振兴杯”全国青年职业技能大赛 国安新桥影视基地艺术家喜获佳绩', '第十三届“振兴杯”全国青年职业技能大赛中，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地选派的3位年轻的特效艺术家取得了优异的竞赛成绩，为中信集团增光添彩。', 'd5e6ad8b4be7038869f8547f7f777d39.jpg', 'd5e6ad8b4be7038.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;">8月21日，由共青团中央、人力资源和社会保障部联合主办的2017年中国技能大赛——第十三届“振兴杯”全国青年职业技能大赛决赛在辽宁沈阳举行。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504569587624825.jpg" title="1504569587624825.jpg" alt="1.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">按照中央金融团工委要求，由中信集团团委选派优秀中信青年技工代表中央金融系统参赛。经遴选，集团团委组建了由中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地和中信戴卡股份有限公司组成的</span>9人代表分别参与了动画制作、模具工、数控车工等项目的比赛，集团团委书记邹江宏担任领队。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(46, 117, 181); letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">最终，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地的王宇、高振江、王志渊获得了</span>3D组第二名、动画制作员第四名的好成绩，中信集团获优秀组织奖。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(46, 117, 181); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504569600287493.jpg" title="1504569600287493.jpg" alt="2.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21px;">对于本次大赛，队长王宇介绍道：“这次大赛，我们的对手都是从各省市经过层层选拔而来的行业精英，我们能取得这样的好成绩，一个重要的诀窍，就是‘快’！”据悉，本次动画项目比赛的制作时间仅有15小时，选手需要在15小时内完成包括从剧本、设计、建模、动画到最终渲染等全部流程的制作，“也是由于有这么一个很短的时间限制，所以比赛的难度极大的提升了，”队员王志渊说道，“我们从早晨7点开始进行剧本的设计，没有一刻休息，直到晚上22点比赛结束，才终于完成了整部动画。由于时间紧迫，其实很多支参赛队伍都没能在规定时间内完成制作。”对于获奖作品，队员高振江介绍到：“此次动画项目比赛的要求是体现大国工匠的精神，以互助为主题，创作动画短片。我们也是根据今年建军90周年这一背景，创作了一部以歼20的研发为主题的动画短片，希望有机会能与大家分享。”<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504569614254815.jpg" title="1504569614254815.jpg" alt="3.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;">第十三届“振兴杯”全国青年职业技能大赛是中国技能大赛的重要组成部分，属于国家级一类职业技能竞赛，被称为青年技能人才的年度“高考”，大赛以“强化质量意识&nbsp;培养大国工匠”为主题，突出“青春质造&nbsp;匠心筑梦”的时代精神，设置动画制作员、数控车工、模具工、汽车装调工等4个竞赛项目。自今年5月大赛启动以来，各地区、行业、系统和大型企业积极组织省级初赛，覆盖工种广泛，参与青年众多。经过层层选拔，来自全国28个省（区、市），金融、煤炭、钢铁等3个行业（系统），15个中央企业和大型企业的331名选手入围决赛，78名裁判为大赛提供权威评判，裁判、选手比例为历届最高，确保竞赛公平公正。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504569627538931.jpg" title="1504569627538931.jpg" alt="4.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;">“振兴杯”大赛得到了中信集团和子公司领导的高度重视，要求团组织以国家级大赛为契机开展青工岗位练兵活动，提高岗位技能，力争获得佳绩。赛前，中信集团团委与参赛的其他国企团委充分交流，学习参赛经验，并与参赛选手充分沟通比赛细节，为其加油鼓劲。中信国安集团有限公司和中信戴卡股份有限公司在收到相关通知后，在人力、物力、财力和时间上给予了大力支持，第一时间进行职业技能水平筛查，选择理论功底扎实、技术能力过硬的青年技工参加大赛。其中，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地的高振江、王志渊、王宇作为优秀的青年艺术家，曾在基地参与过多部影视剧的特效制作，包括《大闹天竺》、《二代妖精》、《时间牢笼》、《幻城》、《凤凰无双》、《武动乾坤》等。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504569641404169.jpg" title="1504569641404169.jpg" alt="5.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;">“振兴杯”有效激发了广大青年职工学技术、练技能的热情，也为优秀青年技能人才的脱颖而出提供了绿色通道。在大赛决赛团队赛及个人赛中获相应名次的选手，经人力资源社会保障部核准后,&nbsp;授予“全国技术能手”荣誉称号，符合条件的，晋升技师或高级工职业资格。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504569818331953.jpg" title="1504569818331953.jpg" alt="6.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;">“振兴杯”大赛举办十三届以来，全国31个省(区、市)及金融、铁道、民航、煤炭、钢铁、汽车等行业系统共举办省级青工技能竞赛超过3000场，市级竞赛超过1.2万场，累计1300多万名青年技术工人参加各级竞赛，超过22万名青年通过技能竞赛活动晋升技术等级，在青年职工中形成了“技能成才、岗位建功”的良好导向。通过“振兴杯”大赛这一平台，中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地输送了人才，锻炼了队伍，基地选派的3位年轻的特效艺术家不畏强手，沉着应战，凭借前期扎实的训练和过硬的心理素质取得了优异的竞赛成绩，充分展现了中信青年的技能水平和拼搏精神，为中信集团增光添彩。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 24px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170905/1504569832988548.jpg" title="1504569832988548.jpg" alt="7.jpg"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(46, 117, 181); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 40px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安新桥影视特效产业基地位于京津冀核心区的中信国安第一城内，距北京城区仅四十公里，距天津城区六十公里。基地建筑面积约三万平方米，全部功能布局和技术标准均由好莱坞专家指导、国内顶尖行业专家参与设计。基地致力于打造全流程的影视制作服务体系，配备了国际一流的全数字、网络化、集群化的电影特效制作硬件以及影视后期音视频制作系统。包括大型数字摄影棚、动作捕捉棚、虚拟绿幕棚、杜比全景声混录棚、交响乐录音棚、DI调色棚、动效棚、对白棚、音视频剪辑工作站、特效后期制作区和特效集群渲染等。依托功能完善的中信国安第一城，基地同时为客户提供影视拍摄、制作、餐饮、住宿等一体化服务。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2017-08-31');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(91, '布局人才战略，中信国安拓展影视行业新高地', '9月19日，中信国安集团与北京电影学院在位于国安第一城的中信国安新桥影视基地举行了隆重的战略合作签约仪式。这次签约旨在整合双方的国际国内优质产业和人才资源，共同推动中信国安影视城的建设和发展。', '8b6ab5654de398d35a4887ab60dbca92.jpg', '8b6ab5654de398d.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 31px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(217, 217, 217); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">用世界的语言&nbsp;讲中国的故事 |&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(217, 217, 217); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">www.vfxcity.com</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 31px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(217, 217, 217); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170920/1505869163592801.png" title="1505869163592801.png" alt="image.png" width="757" height="609"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">9</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">月19日，中信国安集团与北京电影学院在位于国安第一城的中信国安新桥影视基地举行了隆重的战略合作签约仪式。这次签约旨在整合双方的国际国内优质产业和人才资源，共同推动中信国安影视城的建设和发展。本次战略合作的达成标志着中信国安集团正式将电影产业作为集团重点发展的产业项目。在此之前，由国安集团入股的国奥控股集团也已和北京电影学院签署了相关合作协议，目前正在怀柔中国影都区域建设中小学影视教育以及影视基地项目。本次签约和中信国安影视产业基地的落成都标志着中信国安集团拓展影视文化产业新高地的战略布局初步形成。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170920/1505869196923933.png" title="1505869196923933.png" alt="image.png" width="759" height="643"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安集团党委书记夏桂兰致欢迎辞</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">近年来，中国电影市场迎来了产量、票房和观影人次的持续增长，然而，即使头顶全球第二大电影市场的光环，也难掩中国电影工业基础的薄弱。动辄数亿投资的影视项目，还时常靠临时拼凑的团队来制作，其中的专业人才更是占比甚低。因此才有业界专家表示，目前我国影视产业虽然作品产量与日俱增，但是精品力作相对较少、整体竞争力不足的原因，就是人才短板引发的不良效应。人才培养日益成为影视行业实现跨越式发展的关键点和突破口。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">秉持“人才是产业发展核心要素”的经营理念，中信国安集团在完成了影视制作领域重资产的投资之后，再次瞄准了行业痛点。选择行业最优的合作伙伴，这是中信国安一贯的产业突进模式，所以这次的合作对象就是世界著名的北京电影学院。中信国安集团与北京电影学院战略伙伴关系建立后，今年将有十部北京电影学院学子拍摄的影片在中信国安新桥影视基地完成。同时，双方将共同在教育培训、科研开发、影视制作、影视产业孵化等方面开展全方位、多角度的深度合作，为共同推动中国影视文化产业的发展，培养更多高素质、高技能的</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">影视高端专业人才</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://www.vfxcity.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170920/1505869232180649.png" title="1505869232180649.png" alt="image.png" width="731" height="545"/><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安集团与北京电影学院的战略合作签约仪式，在位于京东香河的中信国安第一城内举行，这里新近落成了集影棚拍摄、特效制作、电影音视频后期制作为一体的高端影视制作基地。北京电影学院党委书记侯光明在致辞中表示，中信国安集团作为国内知名的大型综合性企业集团，布局电影产业的决心和力度有目共睹。依托</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安第一城”影视基地作为载体，结合北京电影学院的影视人才、学术成果和产业资源，发挥各自优势，双方将共同建立“产学研”校企合作伙伴关系。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">随着中信国安集团携手北京电影学院共建中信国安影视城的战略举措逐步实施，校企合作将成为培养高端实用型电影人才的最佳路径。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170920/1505869307967430.png" title="1505869307967430.png" alt="image.png" width="1" height="1"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">活动现场，中信国安集团与北京电影学院</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">举行了签约和揭牌仪式，双方在</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安新桥影视基地挂牌设立“北京电影学院教学实训基地”，未来将开展影视制作、教学交流、实习与就业、专业及课程建设、影视产业孵化等全方位的合作。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170920/1505869270475348.png" title="1505869270475348.png" alt="image.png" width="1" height="1"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px;">发布会现场还同时举行了由中信国安集团与北京电影学院青年电影制片厂联合拍摄的公益主题电影《150小时+》开机仪式。据悉，这是一部充满实验性质的“即兴电影”，由北京电影学院副校长孙立军监制，该片将在青海格尔木取景拍摄，主要讲述了形色各异的户外跑爱好者们挑战“生命禁区”——柴达木盆地，筹集善款为乡村小学修建生活配套设施匮乏的故事。配合公益电影主题，中信国安集团还在开机仪式现场表示，将捐资120万元，用于改善云南和青海偏远地区乡村学校支边女教师生活卫生设施。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170920/1505869351340253.png" title="1505869351340253.png" alt="image.png" width="762" height="533"/><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 32px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">《150小时+》是中信国安投资制作的第一部公益主题电影，这部影片的拍摄开启了中信国安独家投资院线电影的先河，这也是为中国新学院派领军人物奉献爱心和生命的作品提供创作支持。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170920/1505869380499205.png" title="1505869380499205.png" alt="image.png" width="774" height="637"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 31px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">北京电影学院党委书记侯光明、北京电影学院副校长孙立军、北京电影学院研究生院院长黄英侠</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，北京电影学院管理学院院长吴曼芳等相关领导；</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安集团董事长李士林、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安集团党委书记夏桂兰、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安集团监事会主席秦永忠、中信国安集团董事李建一、中信国安集团总经理刘鑫、中信国安集团副总经理杜军、中信国安集团工会主席刘欣、中信国安集团董事会执行委员会办公室主任闫宗侠、中信国安集团副总经理崔明宏、中信国安集团纪委书记高智明等集团领导以及来自影视界行业精英近200人共同参加了战略签约仪式和电影新闻发布会。</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>', '0', '2017-09-20'),
(92, '胡玫导演将拍电影《红楼梦》', '9月25日，由胡玫执导的全新电影版《红楼梦》在北京举行新闻发布会暨演员全球海选启动发布会，宣布中国古典四大名著之首《红楼梦》将再现大银幕。', 'c96d41defc360b3145d32d2e9c913ccf.jpg', 'c96d41defc360b3.jpeg', '20180809', '<section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style="padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;9月25日，由胡玫执导的全新电影版《红楼梦》在北京举行新闻发布会暨演员全球海选启动发布会，宣布中国古典四大名著之首《红楼梦》将再现大银幕。导演胡玫、出品人侯光明、李万寿携编剧何燕江、视觉总监赵小丁、美术指导霍廷霄、音乐监制及作曲叶小钢亮相。发布会上，胡玫导演透露早在十年前就想拍摄电影《红楼梦》，此次将以一个全新的角度切入，打造电影《红楼梦》系列三部曲。除此之外，为了更加贴近原著中主要人物的设定，影片的演员将通过全球海选的方式产生，为观众打造耳目一新的视觉体验。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; white-space: pre-wrap; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28.44px; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467046116516.jpg" alt="97e7258a41c742aeac9cd675fcd3c48e.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467046116516.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467093206572.jpeg" alt="2.jpeg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467093206572.jpeg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467101616823.jpeg" alt="3.jpeg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467101616823.jpeg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467108736858.jpg" alt="4.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467108736858.jpg"/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><section><p style="padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;">&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: left; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 0);">胡玫十年磨一剑聚超强班底再续“红楼一梦”</span></strong></p></section><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2em; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 《红楼梦》作为中国古典四大名著之首，是举世公认的中国古典小说巅峰之作，从古至今征服了无数的读者。此次在北京举行的新电影《红楼梦》新闻发布会上，胡玫导演携编剧何燕江、视觉总监赵小丁、美术指导霍廷霄、音乐总监及作曲叶小钢一同揭晓了电影的概念海报，并宣布新电影版《红楼梦》正式启动。从《雍正王朝》、《汉武大帝》、《乔家大院》到《孔子》、《曹操》，胡玫导演以其磅礴大气而温暖细腻的历史视角，打造了一部部经典，获誉无数。而对于此次执导新电影《红楼梦》，胡玫导演坦言“《红楼梦》是我的青春”，并透露早在十年前就有把它搬上大银幕的计划，她表示：“《红楼梦》的故事充满了人生的玄机，文化社会内涵极其丰富。每一次读都有不同的感悟，想把它拍出来给大家分享。”如今项目启动，胡玫导演也颇为感慨，并透露此次将拍摄电影《红楼梦》系列三部曲，会以一个充满了青春活力的全新的角度切入。</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2em; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 为了自己的圆梦之作，胡玫导演特意请来老搭档、著名编剧何燕江执笔，何燕江导演曾经参与打造过《乔家大院》、《孔子》、《曹操》等优秀影视作品。谈及对《红楼梦》的全新改编，何燕江坦言难度很大，并逗趣表示这次的改编是一个“千锤百炼，九死一生”的过程，整个剧本经过很多次大的改写才基本定型。除此以外，编剧组还特意邀请到红学专家为剧本保驾护航，力求贴近原著，可见其精雕细琢。同时，曾联手助力张艺谋导演呈现过《英雄》、《十面埋伏》、《满城尽带黄金甲》等视觉盛宴的摄影指导赵小丁和美术指导霍廷霄，此次也加入到新电影《红楼梦》的主创团队中，分别担任视觉总监和美术指导为影片创作增砖添瓦。赵小丁导演透露这一版《红楼梦》将用到实景拍摄加特效处理的方式，精心再现大观园的风貌；霍廷霄也坦言由于《红楼梦》的故事发生朝代无从考证，在美术设计上将会是一次想象力的激情挑战。而刚刚在第31届中国电影金鸡奖上凭借《开罗宣言》获得最佳音乐奖的著名作曲家叶小钢，这次也以音乐监制及作曲的身份加盟，他表示：“参与《红楼梦》也是我自己的梦，我希望这个梦能够更灿烂的实现。”</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2em; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2em; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 0);">《红楼梦》演员全球海选开启 200课时培训打造新一代红楼人</span></strong></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2em; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2em; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;曹雪芹笔下的《红楼梦》创造了形形色色的人物形象，无论是多愁善感的林黛玉，反封建的叛逆青年贾宝玉，藏愚守拙的美人薛宝钗、两面三刀的王熙凤、外慈内狠的王夫人等等，无不血肉饱满、个性鲜明，这也使得新电影《红楼梦》的选角备受关注。对此，胡玫导演表示《红楼梦》是全世界华人心中的爱，原著中的人物年龄基本都在20岁以下，为了忠实于原著，选到最合适的演员，将拓宽选角渠道，利用海选的方式进行筛选。无论是职业演员或者是素人，无论身处国内还是海外都可参加。发布会现场，北京电影学院副院长孙立军也作为本次海选及培训活动的负责人出席，并介绍会有专家团队来负责演员的筛选。据悉，出品人李万寿是协同资本的董事长，他当场表示对于新版《红楼梦》将不遗余力地提供资金支持。而全部入选演员必须进行100课时的表演培训和100课时国学、红学文化传统封闭式培训，以提高新人演员各方面的能力和素质适应拍摄和角色。全部拍摄及培训将在中信国安的天下第一城制作完成，外景将在扬州、苏州、上海松江等地选取。&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2em; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;《红楼梦》曾诞生过大量影视作品改编版本，其中1987年电视剧版的选角呈现更是征服万千观众，让人称道。谈及此次新电影《红楼梦》的演员全球海选，胡玫导演表示：“希望通过这次的海选，能够挖掘出代表现在这个时代的新红楼人，世界各地的华人都可报名，希望新电影《红楼梦》也是对下一代年轻人的一次古典文化洗礼。”发布会现场，中国著名音乐家、钢琴大师刘诗昆为发布会即兴演奏了两首钢琴曲，著名歌唱家郁钧剑也现场献唱，将气氛推至高潮。著名演员张凯丽也在发布会为好朋友胡玫导演助阵，并表示：“胡玫导演既具备男性导演的坚毅，又有女性的柔美、风韵，我相信这部新电影《红楼梦》一定不会辜负大家。”除此之外，中国著名书法家、北京书法学校校长胡滨先生为新电影《红楼梦》送上了亲自题写的片名书法作品。而随着新电影《红楼梦》演员全球海选海报的揭晓，网上报名通道也已全面打开，选手可通过新电影红楼梦.com官方网站按照提示步骤参与报名。</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2em; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 电影《红楼梦》由上海金德影业有限公司、北京乾坤星光文化传媒有限公司、北京麦特文化发展有限公司出品，北京电影学院、电影频道、中信国安第一城、协同资本、万新集团、中民香山(天津)文化投资有限公司联合出品。据悉，电影《红楼梦》接下来将进入到紧锣密鼓的演员海选工作中，敬请期待新一代红楼人的诞生。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467121180991.jpg" alt="5.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467121180991.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467131186608.jpg" alt="6.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467131186608.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467138728049.jpg" alt="7.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467138728049.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467168705681.jpg" alt="8.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467168705681.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467174744862.jpg" alt="9.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467174744862.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467179189221.jpg" alt="10.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467179189221.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467186588388.jpg" alt="11.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467186588388.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467191924768.jpg" alt="12.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467191924768.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467197595136.jpg" alt="13.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467197595136.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467205409818.jpg" alt="14.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467205409818.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467211159308.jpg" alt="15.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467211159308.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467217527998.jpg" alt="16.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467217527998.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467222659211.jpg" alt="17.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467222659211.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467228476794.jpg" alt="18.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467228476794.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467233275453.jpg" alt="19.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467233275453.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467238202760.jpg" alt="20.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467238202760.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467252815511.jpg" alt="21.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467252815511.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467258352539.jpg" alt="22.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467258352539.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467266417832.jpg" alt="23.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467266417832.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img width="640" height="958" title="1511467272641697.jpg" alt="24.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467272641697.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1511467287773219.jpg" alt="25.webp.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171124/1511467287773219.jpg"/></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; clear: both; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;">文章来源：搜狐</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2017-09-26');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(96, '美国传奇3D公司总裁访问中信国安新桥影视基地', '1月23日，中信国安新桥影视基地总裁屈建平会见了来访的美国传奇3D公司（Legend 3D, Inc.）总裁艾丹• 弗里（Aiden Foley）一行三人，并与美国同行举行了富有建设性的工作会谈。', '66a469223e2228ce3b94eb1f6ec70e80.jpg', '66a469223e2228c.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1月23日，中信国安新桥影视基地总裁屈建平会见了来访的美国传奇3D公司（Legend 3D, Inc.）总裁艾丹• 弗里（Aiden Foley）一行三人，并与美国同行举行了富有建设性的工作会谈。美国传奇3D公司首席市场总监巴里•斯塔格（Barry Stagg）、美国梦想蛋（dreameGGs）影视投资平台总裁童乐（Lorelei Tong）、中信国安文化传媒副总经理高传华、国安新桥影视传媒副总经理杨晓彬、国</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">安新桥影视传媒副总经理黄鹤参加了会谈。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180227/1519704346636675.png" title="1519704346636675.png" alt="blob.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">会谈中，双方就电影3D制作、VR/AR开发、好莱坞电影来华制作、中国本土电影人才培养、影视投资等方面进行沟通并展开讨论。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180227/1519704317537384.png" title="1519704317537384.png" alt="blob.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">弗里先生表示，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">电脑数字图像处理占电影内容制作比重越来越大，而传奇公司主营的立体3D制作、视觉效果创作、VR/AR开发和动画制作四大业务版块的共同点都是利用电脑技术对图像做数字操作处理，相互之间联系紧密。传奇公司希望能与中信国安新桥影视基地合作把主营的四大业务板块复制到中国，推动中美电影界紧密合作，促进中美电影市场共同发展。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">屈总表示，目前中国电影3D制作业务市场潜力巨大，VR/AR等新媒体技术开发前景广阔。希望传奇公司能将好莱坞电影项目引入中国电影基地，引进有好莱坞大片制作经验的人才为各地培训当地人才开展制作业务，使用中国艺术家参与大片制作，促进地方经济结构向国际化转型升级。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180227/1519704284624504.png" title="1519704284624504.png" alt="blob.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在访问中，屈总陪同弗里总裁、斯塔格先生和童乐女士参观了基地3000㎡摄影棚、动作捕捉棚、杜比全景声混录剧院、交响乐录音棚、DI调色棚和杜比7.1声道音频编辑室等基地设施。当他们</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">看到中信国安新桥影视基地配备的</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">先进的电影全流程制作软硬件和中外艺术家组成的电影特效制作团队</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">时，感到十分兴奋。同时，对基地在接待拍摄剧组的标准化管理、影视全产业链配套的相关服务表示赞赏。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180227/1519704252951742.png" title="1519704252951742.png" alt="blob.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">其中，在杜比全景声混录剧院，屈总还与三位贵宾一起欣赏了如临其境的杜比全景声电影片段。贵宾们表示，基地的电影声音制作平台已经处于世界先进水平，希望能与国安新桥有更多方向的合作。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180227/1519704222837838.png" title="1519704222837838.png" alt="blob.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">美国传奇</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3D</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">公司</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">主营立体3D转换、视觉效果、VR/AR和动画制作四大业务版块，与好莱坞各大电影制片公司包括迪士尼、福克斯、哥伦比亚、环球、派拉蒙、传奇、华纳、漫威等建立了长期战略合作关系，参与项目包括《超能敢死队》、《神奇动物在哪里》、《奇异博士》、《超凡蜘蛛侠》以及《加勒比海盗5：死无对证》等。同时，在VR领域，与三星、Oculus、戴尔等硬件供应商达成各项合作。目前</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">美国传奇</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3D</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">公司</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">已在美国洛杉矶、加拿大多伦多、印度浦那等地区设立制作基地，同时未来将在中国建立第一个好莱坞的MPAA技术及安全体系认证基地, 预计将有10家以上国内外著名影视制作公司及工作室入驻, 引入并完成10部以上好莱坞大片的2D转3D制作项目，组建600人规模的创意、设计和制作团队，形成以影视2D转3D、VR/AR制作为主导的产业体系。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180227/1519704169678308.png" title="1519704169678308.png" alt="blob.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(46, 117, 181); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安新桥影视基地</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(46, 117, 181); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">的建设工作目前已完成，即将于</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(46, 117, 181); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2月整体投入使用</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(46, 117, 181); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，基地可提供从影棚及外景场地租赁、后期制作、特效制作、制片协作到住宿餐饮、后勤支持等全方位、高质量的电影制作全流程服务</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(46, 117, 181); letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，敬请期待！</span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2018-01-26'),
(97, '易智互联网学院与中信国安新桥影视基地共同成立创新实践教育中心', '2018年2月2日下午，易智互联网学院与中信国安新桥影视基地共同成立的创新实践教育中心揭牌仪式在北京国际经贸研修学院会议室隆重举行。', '6184ce2058b31bff45c47df71792106f.jpg', '6184ce2058b31bf.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 24px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent: 37px;line-height:150%"><span style=";position:  relative;z-index:1;left:-3px;top:0px;width:554px;height:277px"></span> <span style="font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:仿宋">2018</span><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋">年2月2日下午，易智互联网学院与中信国安新桥影视基地共同成立的创新实践教育中心揭牌仪式在北京国际经贸研修学院会议室隆重举行。北京国际经贸研修学院院长、易智互联（北京）教育科技有限公司联合创始人俞雷，北京国际经贸研修学院副院长孙凤，易智互联（北京）教育科技有限公司联合创始人、执行董事陈汝喜，易智互联（北京）教育科技有限公司联合创始人王丹普，北京国际经贸研修学院教务处处长刘昭，中信国安新桥影视基地副总经理黄鹤，中信国安新桥影视基地教学部总监杨桂民等出席了此次揭牌仪式。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;text-indent:37px;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519957040976377.png" title="1519957040976377.png" alt="image.png"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent: 37px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋">揭牌仪式前，黄鹤总和孙凤院长相继进行了仪式致辞，就此次与北京国际经贸研修学院双方各尽所长达成深度战略合作，给予了美好的愿景。黄鹤表示中国影视后期制作行业属于人才密集型产业，目前人才缺口高达60万，发展潜力巨大，通过产教融合的方式为中国电影后期制作行业输入优秀的艺、技结合的人才，是行业发展必然趋势。孙凤院长也表示创新实践教育中心的成立真正实现学校和企业在课程、师资、管理等方面的资源共享和技术互补，不仅可以推动学校的课程改革及学生培训工作，更可以解决中国影视行业用人需求问题。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519957064624760.png" title="1519957064624760.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent: 37px;line-height:150%">&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 19px;">伴随着热烈的掌声，俞雷院长和公司副总经理黄鹤为创新实践教育中心正式揭牌，此举标志着北京国际经贸研修学院与中信国安新桥影视基地的战略合作关系向更深层次的推进。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent: 37px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋">此后，黄鹤代表中信国安新桥影视基地总经理屈建平先生向学校相关领导表达了问候，并将屈总专门为此次揭牌仪式准备的书法对联作为礼物交付对方。 “冬去山川齐秀丽，春来桃李共芬芳”不仅贴切双方合作的时机正处冬去春来之时，更表示了屈总对此次双方合作的良好祝愿。“百年树人”的横批更是提纲挈领，也是此次祝愿的精华所在，表示教书育人这件事不能着急，做教育其实做的是良心。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519957102963908.png" title="1519957102963908.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent: 37px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋">揭牌仪式后，领导们围绕着“互联网+”影视后期制作方向大学生岗前实训、校企专业共建及此后的合作细项进行了热烈的座谈。陈汝喜先生就之后的教学课程设置、教学管理等问题与中信国安新桥影视基地教学部总监杨桂民进行了交流，杨桂民总监表示“在此后的学生课堂中需要加些通识教育，在加强教学的同时，学生管理必须跟上。这不仅是对学生负责，也是对自己负责”。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent: 37px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋">易智互联网学院是一家致力于促进中国产学研协同发展，从事教育项目运作、教育管理和教育咨询的专业教育服务机构。中信国安新桥影视基地致力于打造全流程的影视制作服务体系，配备了国际一流的电影特效制作硬件以及影视后期音视频制作系统。此外，还具备专业的教学师资团队和国际化教学指导，采用温哥华电影学院的教学模式即教学大纲。此次双方的强强联合，定会为社会培养出更多“互联网+”影视后期制作方向的人才，一同用世界的语言讲中国的故事！</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180302/1519957123307343.png" title="1519957123307343.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 150%;"><br/></p>', '1', '2018-03-02');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(99, '“提升中国电影的制作水准和国际竞争力”论坛 在中信国安新桥影视基地隆重举行', '4月20日下午，第八届北京国际电影节“提升中国电影的制作水准和国际竞争力”论坛在中信国安新桥影视基地隆重举行。', 'd5bb18b5ff6b58f88b1109ef0cd7c0ca.jpg', 'd5bb18b5ff6b58f.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(214, 214, 214);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">用世界的语言</span>&nbsp;讲中国的故事 |&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); background: rgb(214, 214, 214); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">www.vfxcity.com</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 14px; background: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">近年来，随着中国电影产业的强劲发展，票房屡创新高，但中国电影无论是制作水准、市场表现，还是海外影响力却仍旧差强人意。因此，如何提升中国电影的制作水准和国际竞争力也成为了热门讨论话题。受北京国际电影节组委会的委托，</span>4月20<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">日下午，围绕这一话题，第八届北京国际电影节</span>“提升中国电影的制作水准和国际竞争力”论坛在中信国安新桥影视基地<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">隆重举行，本场论坛堪称本次电影节期间最有成效和影响力的论坛之一。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620652232897.jpg" title="1524620652232897.jpg" alt="1.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">本次论坛汇聚了包括著名导演米家山、北京电影学院副校长孙立军、美国传奇</span>3D公司副总裁Will Maurer、一九零五影业（北京）有限公司总经理李伊、大盛国际传媒集团执行副总裁刘璐、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中国新闻出版传媒集团有限公司项目规划管理部主任李焰、聚禾影画传媒（北京）股份有限公司董事长刘畅等来自国内外电影界的一线的投资人、导演、制片人、专家学者共计</span>100<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">余代表，共同研讨行业趋势、剖析电影市场、加强国际交流，实现资源和信息的对接交流，搭建合作平台。在论坛开始之前，著名导演米家山接受了中信国安新桥影视基地总裁屈建平颁发的聘书，受邀成为基地的艺术顾问。与此同时，</span>“青少年国际电影筑梦计划”暨影视实训基地合作协议和“<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安新桥影视基地与北京电影学院（河北）培训中心合作协议</span>”也在基地完成签署。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620657566697.jpg" title="1524620657566697.jpg" alt="2.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">本次论坛由中信国安文化传媒有限公司、国安新桥（北京）影视传媒投资有限公司共同主办，北京国际电影节组委会、国家广播电视总局、中汇新视（北京）科技文化传媒有限公司、聚禾影画传媒（北京）股份有限公司、共青团中央网络影视中心、瑞丹斯电影机构（英国）鼎力支持。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620662695066.jpg" title="1524620662695066.jpg" alt="3.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">论坛由中信国安新桥影视基地创始人屈建平主持，中信国安集团副总经理、中信国安文化传媒有限公司董事长崔明宏与会并致辞。崔明宏表示，中信国安集团长期致力于创新业务发展，在国家倡导文化产业繁荣发展的新时期，积极拓展影视全产业链开发。本届论坛秉承“坚定文化自信，推动中国文化走出去”的活动宗旨，探索提升中国电影的制作水准和国际竞争力的路径和方法，将以创新引领发展的思维模式，搭建起国内外影视界沟通交流的平台。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620666741501.jpg" title="1524620666741501.jpg" alt="4.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;">中国电影应尽快打造坚实的工业标准和工业基础</span></strong><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为了促进思想交流与观点碰撞，论坛设置了三大议题。在“中国电影如何建立高标准制作平台”这一议题中，著名导演米家山、美国Legend 3D公司副总裁Will Maurer、美国Legend 3D公司中国董事童乐女士、著名导演郭大群、著名导演陈楚童、索尼公司前技术导师Keith Collea、著名导演陈心中进行了深入探讨，大家将国内制作公司与国外行业霸主进行对比，针对中外差距等问题进行了深入解读，并对提升国内电影的制作标准等提出建议与期许。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620674849908.jpg" title="1524620674849908.jpg" alt="5.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;">中国电影人才要在产业中培养</span></strong><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">当前中国电影人才短缺的情况非常突出，无法适应中国电影市场高速发展的人才需求。因此，在</span>“中国电影如何培养创新型制作人才”这一议题中，主办方邀请了北京电影学院副校长孙立军、加拿大温哥华电影学院中国办公室主任许建红、韩国影像物等级委员会委员|庆熙大学电影专业学部长姜乃英、北京电影学院河北培训中心主任袁成、中华两岸文创发展协会创始理事陈朝平、著名导演<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">摄影师</span>|<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">史岳、中央美术学院设计学院数码媒体工作室副教授陈卓作为嘉宾进行讨论。在讨论中，大家各抒己见，针对</span>“中国电影产业升级中的专业人才危机”、“中国电影教育和产业之间的脱节”等问题进行了深入剖析。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620680476377.jpg" title="1524620680476377.jpg" alt="6.jpg"/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;">中国电影应建立更加规范化、系统化的融资模式</span></strong><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中国电影已经与资本之间形成了越来越紧密的联系，但资本的这种介入又必须是理性且有序的。因此</span>“中国电影如何建立良好的投资制作环境”这一该议题邀请了中信国安西藏创新基金总经理张建科、一九零五影业（北京）有限公司总经理李伊、大盛国际传媒集团执行副总裁刘璐、路恩国际CEO创始人Jonathan Garrison、天驰君泰律师事务所合伙人张继志、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">聚禾影画传媒（北京）股份有限公司董事长刘畅、中国电影艺术研究中心</span>|中国电影资料馆研究馆员苗禾、保利影业投资有限公司制片人沙笑如，嘉宾们围绕“当电影或主动或被动地得到资本的助推，市场是否会更加热闹繁荣”等问题进行了共同讨论。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620685336993.jpg" title="1524620685336993.jpg" alt="7.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">论坛结束后，举行了</span>“青少年国际电影筑梦计划”暨影视实训基地合作签约仪式，现场发布了由<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">共青团中央网络影视中心、中汇新视（北京）科技文化传媒有限公司、瑞丹斯电影机构（英国）、聚禾影画传媒（北京）股份有限公司、国安新桥（北京）影视传媒投资有限公司共同打造的</span>“青少年国际电影筑梦计划”。该计划旨在为优秀青少年文化人才的培养提供专业的交流平台、深入的影视知识、完备的实践基地及迈向更广阔的国际舞台的机会。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620699284768.jpg" title="1524620699284768.jpg" alt="8.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在活动的最后，还进行了中信国安新桥影视基地与北京电影学院（河北）培训中心的合作协议签约仪式，今后双方将成立专项机构，共同探索建立影视产业体系全新的教学模式、评价体系和运行机制，把北京电影学院的影视职业人才培训与就业相结合，借助北京电影学院的强大教育优势，让中信国安新桥影视基地成为京津冀地区影视特色教育及就业示范区。同时，配合中信国安新桥影视基地打造以资本驱动产业创新的电影产业运营模式的布局，共同打造产业形态创新、金融服务创新的国际化电影投资和制作项目，构建国际化的影视全产业链运营平台。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524620704852759.jpg" title="1524620704852759.jpg" alt="9.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在本次论坛中，国内外电影界的各路精英、专家学者汇聚一堂，各抒己见，对于快速发展中的中国电影工业，如何借鉴国际先进的电影理念与技术，进一步提升中国电影的制作水准，迎接中国电影大制作时代的到来，意义深远。在文化产业快速成长的今天，国安新桥目前已完成了国际水准的影视基地建设，作为国内目前最先进的电影全流程制作平台，基地配备了国际一流的全数字、网络化、集群化的电影前期拍摄、特效制作及影视后期音视频制作系统，涵盖了数字摄影棚、动作捕捉棚、绿幕抠像棚、电影调色棚、音乐录音棚、杜比全景声混录棚以及特效后期制作区、集群渲染区等。为满足影视行业的版权保护需求，基地参照美国电影协会标准，建设了封闭内网环境下的大型数据存储中心。与此同时，国安新桥还将携手海内外力量，共同打造中国文化元素的、面向国际市场的系列影片，期待未来中国电影能成功走上世界银幕，让更多全球观众领略中国文化悠久的历史和永恒的魅力。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2018-04-24'),
(100, '米家山导演受聘担任中信国安新桥影视基地艺术顾问', '4月20日下午，中国著名导演米家山先生正式受聘成为中信国安新桥影视基地的艺术顾问。', '6dac5df65f03ef47a97a1998a2f8ab16.jpg', '6dac5df65f03ef4.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(214, 214, 214);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">用世界的语言</span>&nbsp;讲中国的故事 |&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); background: rgb(214, 214, 214); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">www.vfxcity.com</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">4月20日下午，第八届北京国际电影节“提升中国电影的制作水准和国际竞争力”论坛在中信国安新桥影视基地成功举办。一百余名国内外影视界投资人、制片人和制作精英与会，分别就如何提高中国影视制作水准、创新人才培训和电影投资环境展开讨论。中国著名导演米家山先生出席论坛并正式受聘成为中信国安新桥影视基地的艺术顾问。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524621719698951.jpg" title="1524621719698951.jpg" alt="2.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安新桥影视基地创始人屈建平先生回忆起80年代初与米家山导演在北京电影学院度过的同窗时光，二人志同道合情同手足，他非常感谢米家山导演给自己分享宝贵的经验与艺术理想。更感谢米导在自己回国与中信国安集团合作创建的影视基地给予全力投入和支持。他相信与米导和其他电影学院同窗的密切合作，势必将会为中信国安新桥影视基地注入强大的创作活力和力量。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524621798279079.jpg" title="1524621798279079.jpg" alt="1.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">米家山导演也表示，他深信与中信国安新桥影视基地的合作不是一纸空文，这将是他的使命所在。同时，他今后影片的拍摄与制作，也均将在基地进行。米家山导演非常认同基地“用世界的语言，讲中国的故事”这一理念。他认为基地拥有国内目前最先进、最完善的电影全流程制作平台，为提高电影品质奠定了坚实的基础。基地的创建，将改变中国电影市场对电影品质，尤其是对后期制作忽视乃至漠视的现状，有助于推动中国电影走向世界。同时，基地也为有创意、有才华的年轻导演提供了多角度、全方位的创作及交流平</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">台。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524621816466183.jpg" title="1524621816466183.jpg" alt="5.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">米家山导演是中国殿堂级导演。几十年来，他坚持创作，认为电影的发展不仅在于屏幕数量的增长，更在于电影内容本身是否深入到各个受众群体。他对待剧本严谨认真，精益求精，曾用七年多的时间对一个剧本进行深入创作。他执导的电视剧处女作《弯弯的石径》，曾获第3届中国电视剧“飞天奖”一等奖。凭借喜剧电影《顽主》，米家山导演还曾提名第9届中国电影金鸡奖最佳导演奖。也正是因为这部电影，他被称为张国立、葛优、梁欢等一系列优秀演员真正意义上的“伯乐”。著名导演冯小刚曾表示，他很感谢米家山导演，《顽主》是对他影响最大的中国电影。冯导的《私人订制》正是对《顽主》的致敬。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180425/1524621833970897.jpg" title="1524621833970897.jpg" alt="4.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">最后，屈建平总经理表示，基地将与米家山导演推出一系列优秀作品，以其卓越的创作才能，将带领基地走向更高、更好的发展。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2018-04-24');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(102, '著名导演黄健中<br/>考察中信国安新桥影视基地', '5月7日，中国著名导演黄健中考察了位于中信国安第一城的中信国安新桥影视基地。中信国安新桥影视基地CEO屈建平陪同黄健中导演考察了已投入使用的基地前期拍摄和后期制作设施。', 'a33cb87e48e2104e5ec6a6a38e7277b2.jpg', 'a33cb87e48e2104.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(214, 214, 214);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">用世界的语言</span>&nbsp;讲中国的故事 |&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-decoration: underline; line-height: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); background: rgb(214, 214, 214); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">www.vfxcity.com</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">5</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">月7日，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中国著名导演黄健中</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">考察了位于中信国安第一城的中信国安新桥影视基地。中信国安新桥影视基地CEO屈建平陪同黄健中导演考察了已投入使用的基地前期拍摄和后期制作设施。黄</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">健</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">中导演对基地的高标准配置和先进的管理系统表示肯定。他对基地秉持“用世界的语言，讲中国的故事”表示高度赞扬。作为中国新时期电影的代表人物，黄导演表示将和基地展开深度合作，带领基地的青年团队为中国电影走向世界贡献力量。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: white;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180514/1526289103493458.jpg" title="1526289103493458.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514171057.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: start; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">黄健中导演首先考察了基地一期影视特效制作区。看到新桥影视基地朝气蓬勃的特效艺术家团队和京东最大的特效渲染农场，黄导表示满意。黄导对基地二期先进的电影全产业链制作集群更是赞不绝口。黄导演在听取屈建平总经理有关基地“用世界的语言，讲中国的故事”的发展使命时表示赞同说：“中国电影艺术家如果没有接受新的数字电影技术语言，就会跟不上新时代的要求。基地全新的电影制作设施和先进的流程管理系统，一定能够助力中国电影走向世界的第四次高峰的到来。”他明确表示要在中信国安新桥影视基地完成接下来的多部影视作品的创作和后期制作。屈总表示欢迎黄健中导演来基地拍摄电影和电视剧，并期待黄导能带领基地为中国电影打开世界的天窗做出贡献。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 40px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180514/1526289135669880.jpg" title="1526289135669880.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514171104.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color:#333333;font-family:Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">著名剧作家池敬嘉、制片人付红</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">等人随同黄健中导演实地考察了中信国安</span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">新桥</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">影视</span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">基地，并在基地音频编辑室观摩了杜比声效编辑，在180㎡调色棚观看了3D电影效果演示。国安新桥影视传媒投资有限公司副总经理杨晓彬、孙东光、黄鹤等领导陪同屈建平总经理出席了会见。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180514/1526289222432077.jpg" title="1526289222432077.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514171111.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;黄健中导演是中国影视艺术界为数不多的优秀艺术家之一。作为中国第四代导演的中坚人物，他以多变的风格一直活跃在影视创作的一线。黄健中导演1960年进入北京电影制片厂附属电影学校学习。先后担任场记、副导演、导演等工作。从电影《小花》、《如意》到《良家妇女》，从《一个死者对生者的访问》到《龙年警官》、《过年》，从《大鸿米店》、《红娘》到《我的1919》，从电视剧《笑傲江湖》到《海棠依旧》，在黄健中导演30多年的艺术创作生涯中，几乎没有固定的模式和套路，永远以一个年轻人的心态在不断前行，探索和追求着影视艺术的真谛。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180514/1526289264789246.jpg" title="1526289264789246.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514171116.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;黄健中导演执导的电影《良家妇女》1986年获第二十五届卡罗维发利国际电影节主要奖和国际影评家组织奖，西班牙第十八届大西洋国际电影节最佳影片奖、安达鲁西亚电影家协会评论奖、西班牙电影俱乐部奖，比利时皇家电影博物馆、资料馆发掘新电影奖，1987年获第十一届印度电影节国际评论家奖。此外，他执导的《龙年警官》、《过年》分别获广播电影电视部1989－1990、1991年优秀影片奖，第十四、十五届电影百花奖最佳故事片奖。《过年》并于1992年获第四届东京国际电影节国际评委奖。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180514/1526289278668783.jpg" title="1526289278668783.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514171120.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;黄健中导演非常认同基地“用世界的语言，讲中国的故事”这一理念。他认为基地拥有国内目前最先进、最完善的电影全流程制作平台，为提高电影制作品质奠定了坚实的基础。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180514/1526289303869119.jpg" title="1526289303869119.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514171124.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;中信国安新桥影视基地将携手黄健中导演，共同打造高质量的、面向国际市场的影视剧集，期待未来在基地制作的影视作品能走上世界屏幕，让更多全球观众领略中国电影的独特魅力。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2018-05-09');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(103, '国安新桥携手高级调色师<br/>用色彩点亮光影世界', '近日，中信国安新桥影视基地签约了台湾资深高级调色师张明珠，为今后的长期合作奠定了良好基础。', '1336e1034af90f7d13de25d53709d0ed.jpg', '1336e1034af90f7.jpeg', '20180809', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 17);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: rgb(229, 229, 229); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">用世界的语言&nbsp;讲中国的故事 |&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: rgb(229, 229, 229); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">www.vfxcity.com</span></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 25.5px;  box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; widows: 1;近日，中信国安新桥影视基地签约了台湾资深高级调色师张明珠，为今后的长期合作奠定了良好基础。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">明珠拥有超过20年资历的调色生涯，以优异的色感，娴熟的技巧，深受导演与摄影师以及各大后期公司的喜爱。她曾与邓超、黄信尧等导演合作，更是台湾导演黄中平先生与钟孟宏先生长期指定合作的调色师。除此之外，明珠也同时身为王菲、孙燕姿、周杰伦、张惠妹等华语一线歌手的MV调色师。其作品还涉及电视广告、短片。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180515/1526355748920961.jpg" title="1526355748920961.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514163430.jpg" width="719" height="486"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">图为张明珠，摄于台湾现代电影</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 192px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 192px; line-height: 25.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">即便已经得到业界的高度关注与认可，明珠仍孜孜不倦于持续学习进修。她曾分别在英国与新加坡的International Colorist Academy（国际调色师学院）学习进修调色相关理论与应用，也曾在美国Company3调色公司观摩见习，学习各式各样的数码调色软件。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180515/1526355815562390.jpg" title="1526355815562390.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514163443.jpg" width="716" height="555"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">与邓超、俞白眉导演，摄于北京PO朝霆</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 32px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 25.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从业以来，明珠的工作足迹更是遍布中国、东南亚及欧美地区。她曾为《<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 17);">西游记女儿国》《恶棍天使》《痞子英雄2》《北京纽约》</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 17); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">等电影调色。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;"><br/></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;"><video class="edui-upload-video  vjs-default-skin video-js" controls="" preload="none" width="791" height="475" src="/ueditor/php/upload/video/20180516/1526436690379109.mp4" data-setup="{}"></video></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">明珠作品Showreel</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在影片《恶棍天使》中，明珠面对不可控的天气因素，克服光影匹配连戏困难，运用高超的技巧，为大家呈现出一个色彩丰富、通透的影调，颇具胶片电影质感。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180515/1526356023982170.jpg" title="1526356023982170.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514163453.jpg" width="791" height="475"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">与DP汪大勇老师，摄于北京PO朝霆&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180515/1526356068275455.jpg" title="1526356068275455.jpg" alt="微信图片_20180514163501.jpg" width="786" height="547"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">与邓超老师，摄于北京PO朝霆</span>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">根据明珠多年的从业经验，她发现中国调色人才在质与量上,根本赶不及中国电影产业的飞速成长，因此产业的发展的确有比较奇怪与浮夸的一些现象。举例来说：坊间有训练机构标榜一天10小时，七天成为调色师的广告语。调色师的养成是各种主客观条件俱足才能造就出来的， 除了需要有经验的师傅带领培育所需的色彩原理知识与器材操作， 还需要长时间大量的自我练习学习看waveform（波形）与做黑白平衡的基本功，还有色彩匹配的精确与速度。在掌握技术之后，还要培养与客户的沟通技巧与聆听的能力，这些都不是一蹴可几的事。而且她还发现，年轻一代调色师，几乎很少在看视波仪waveform（波形）与vector scope<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 17);">（</span>矢量示波器），大部份都是在套现成的Lut居多，学习的重点有颠倒的情况。这很容易忽略了对细节与质量，还有肤质透度的把<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 17);"></span>控。然后没有基础又急就章下培养出来的调色师再去培养下一代，未来中国调色师的素质，实在令人担忧。庆幸的是，她最近终于看到有踏实的机构引进ICA(International Colorist Academy)课程。希望这个产业越来越重视质量与基本功的炼就，而不是只是为了商业考量，大量接片，然后丢给资浅的调色师去练手。另一方面，她也期许电影主创者更加重视调色这一个环节。这对于色彩影调质量的严苛要求，对于提升中国电影调色师的素质，避免滥竽充数的现象，绝对能起到作用。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180515/1526356099358371.jpg" title="1526356099358371.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180515/1526356099995603.jpg" title="1526356099995603.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px;">中信国安新桥影视基地调色棚</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 12px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">明珠参观了中信国安新桥影视基地，两间180㎡哈克尼斯（Harkness）Matt Plus大荧幕调色棚，分别引进全球顶级调色系统Baselight TWO、Baselight ONE以及DaVinci Resolve，配备科视（Christie）CP4230全球顶尖4K DLP Digital Cinema投影机，支持高性能浮点渲染，进行2D 4K / 3D 4K实时调色的同时，兼顾画面处理及审看功能，能够多方位契合电影、短片、广告、MV等影像作品的DI工作。她惊讶于基地配备有最熟悉的调色软件达芬奇与原厂大Panel，还有两套业界最期待、最认可的调色软硬件—调色设备中，色彩管理与色彩科学做的最好的Baselight，以及业界顶级的屏幕(10米)与高端的投影设备。 50人座的DI影棚，新颖宽敞又气派，整体环境与硬件设施都是调色师梦想的顶级水平。她也期许未来合作能在流程<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em;">上有更完整与丰富经验的团队基础。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">调色是一门兼具艺术与技术的学问，在与明珠等众多全球顶尖艺术家建立长期合作的基础上，中信国安新桥影视基地拥有国内最先进的调色设备，为高品质调色提供了更多的可能性。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中信国安新桥影视基地将携手明珠，共同打造高质量的、面向国际市场的系列影片，期待未来中国电影能走上世界银幕，让更多全球观众领略中国电影中的多彩世界。</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '2018-05-02');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `title`, `intro`, `img`, `thumb_img`, `img_time`, `cont`, `classify`, `time`) VALUES
(104, '梦回红楼<br/>“红楼梦经典传承”书画艺术展开幕', '2018年10月25日上午，由中信国安静赏轩艺术馆主办，国安新桥（北京）影视传媒投资有限公司支持的“红楼梦经典传承”书画艺术展在中信国安第一城正安宫举行开幕仪式。', '5bd6d44b609d01wq3698tqdbo164dq.jpg', '5bd6d44b609d01w.jpg', '20181029', '<section><section><section><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181029/1540805338103340.png" title="1540805338103340.png" alt="图片.png"/></section></section></section><p><section><section><section><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2018年10月25日上午，由中信国安静赏轩艺术馆主办的“红楼梦经典传承”书画艺术展在中信国安第一城正安宫举行开幕仪式。旨在通过展示不同时代画家基于《红楼梦》的不同理解而创作出的优秀作品，让更多人领略《红楼梦》的艺术魅力，同时弘扬了中华优秀传统文化。</span><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181029/1540805367138730.png" title="1540805367138730.png" alt="图片.png"/><section><br/></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">出席本次活动的领导及嘉宾包括中信国安集团股东会主席李士林先生和百年巨匠总策划李小琳女士，以及众多在红学文化领域卓有建树专家学者。同时，郑希林、金大钧、金万钧、王润、郭凤、车梅、王树忠、崔景哲、付爱民、赵东、廖沙、贾爱英等艺术家也参与了本次开幕式。</p></section></section></section><section><section><section><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181029/1540805406448003.png" title="1540805406448003.png" alt="图片.png"/></section></section></section><section><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">此次展览通过多时空节点的碰撞，重现《红楼梦》这一经典文学著作给人们带来的启迪，推进广大艺术爱好者对经典文学的追求，培养新一代对传统文化的热情。</span></p><section></section><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;"><br/></p></section><section><section><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181029/1540805431387716.png" title="1540805431387716.png" alt="图片.png"/><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181029/1540805547246701.jpg" title="1540805547246701.jpg" alt="微信图片_20181029173151.jpg"/></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section></section></section></section><section><section><section><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181029/1540805577872254.png" title="1540805577872254.png" alt="图片.png"/></section></section><section><section><section><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 3px; line-height: 1.2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(156, 26, 50); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; font-size: 20px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 3px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padd